UI/HotkeyProfileDescription/0_Default,标准的快捷键方案将大多数命令设置在键盘左侧。命令名称的首字母通常就是对应的快捷键。 /// Standard keeps most commands on the left side of the keyboard. The first letter of the command name is often used as the hotkey.=6371
UI/HotkeyProfileDescription/1_NameRightSide,该设置适用于惯用左手的玩家。将大多数命令设置在键盘的右侧。值得注意的不同之处包括：<n/>   - F12同样是跳出键。<n/>   - 聊天快捷键改为Tab键。<n/>   - 编组功能按键由1至0改为3至=。 /// Designed for left-handed players. Keeps most commands on the right side of the keyboard. A few key differences to make note of:<n/>   - The F12 key is an alternate key for Escape.<n/>   - Chat moved to the Tab key.<n/>   - Control Group functionality shifted from the 1 to 0 keys to the 3 to = keys.=6372
UI/HotkeyProfileDescription/2_GridLeftSide,顺序排列的快捷键方案根据按钮在命令面板中的位置进行快捷键的设置。 /// Grid hotkeys are based on the button's position in the command card.=6373
UI/HotkeyProfileDescription/3_GridRightSide,顺序排列的快捷键方案根据按钮在命令面板中的位置进行快捷键的设置。值得注意的不同之处包括：<n/>   - F12同样是跳出键。<n/>   - 聊天快捷键改为Tab键。<n/>   - 编组功能按键由1至0改为3至=。 /// Grid hotkeys are based on the button's position in the command card. A few key differences to make note of:<n/>   - The F12 key is an alternate key for Escape.<n/>   - Chat moved to the Tab key.<n/>   - Control Group functionality shifted from the 1 to 0 keys to the 3 to = keys.=6374
UI/HotkeyProfileDescription/4_Classic,传统的快捷键方案采用《星际争霸》中的快捷键设置（若存在对应的按钮）。 /// Classic uses the hotkeys from the original StarCraft (where possible).=6375

Uploading copyrighted, offensive, or malicious content is against the StarCraft II End User License Agreement and the Blizzard Terms Of Use and can result in disciplinary action that may include complete restriction from the Blizzard service. UI/InputOptionsTooltips/ControlGroupMode,<c val="ffffff">编组：</c><n/>该选项决定了编组按钮的属性。<n/><n/><c val="ffffff">常规：</c>按钮可视且可以点击。<n/><c val="ffffff">隐藏：</c>按钮不可视。<n/><c val="ffffff">不可点击：</c>按钮可视但无法点击。 /// <c val="ffffff">Control Groups:</c><n/>Determines the behavior of Control Group Buttons.<n/><n/><c val="ffffff">Normal:</c> Buttons are visible and can be clicked by the mouse.<n/><c val="ffffff">Hidden:</c> Buttons are not visible.<n/><c val="ffffff">Unclickable:</c> Buttons are visible but can not be clicked by the mouse.=6435
UI/InputOptionsTooltips/CursorConfine,<c val="ffffff">限制鼠标活动范围：</c><n/>该选项决定了鼠标光标在窗口模式(最大化)和窗口模式下是否可以离开应用程序的窗口。在全屏模式下，这项设置没有效果，鼠标光标永远受到限制。<n/><n/><c val="ffffff">智能：</c>在窗口模式(最大化)下，鼠标光标在游戏中将受到限制，但在菜单界面中不受限制。在窗口模式下，这将没有效果。<n/><c val="ffffff">开启：</c>始终进行限制。<n/><c val="ffffff">关闭：</c>从不进行限制。 /// <c val="ffffff">Confine Mouse Cursor:</c><n/>Determines when the mouse cursor can leave the application window in either Windowed (Fullscreen) or Windowed Display Modes.  In the Fullscreen Display Mode this setting has no effect, the cursor is always confined.<n/><n/><c val="ffffff">Smart:</c> In Windowed Fullscreen, mouse cursor is confined during games, but unconfined in menu screens.  In windowed mode, this has no effect.<n/><c val="ffffff">On:</c> Mouse cursor is always confined.<n/><c val="ffffff">Off:</c> Mouse cursor is never confined.=6436

UI/InputOptionsTooltips/QuickCastMode,<c val="ffffff">快速施法：</c><n/>决定攻击和技能的目标锁定机制。<n/><n/><c val="ffffff">关闭：</c>按下快捷键下达指令时进入瞄准模式随后<k pre="(" val="TargetChoose" post=")"/>下达指令。<n/><c val="ffffff">开启：</c>按下快捷键下达指令，方向取决于鼠标指向位置。<n/><c val="ffffff">松开按键时：</c>按下快捷键下达指令进入瞄准模式，然后放开快捷键向鼠标指向位置下达指令。 /// <c val="ffffff">Quick Cast:</c><n/>Determines how attack and ability targeting behaves.<n/><n/><c val="ffffff">Off:</c> Pressing a hotkey to issue an order enters target mode and then <k pre="(" val="TargetChoose" post=")"/> issues the order.<n/><c val="ffffff">On:</c> Pressing a hotkey instantly issues the order in the direction or location of your mouse cursor.<n/><c val="ffffff">On Release:</c> Pressing a hotkey enters targeting mode and releasing the hotkey issues the order in the direction of your mouse cursor.=6447

UI/VideoOptionsInstructions,游戏进行或观看录像时，您可以按下CTRL-F11切换游戏内视频录制的开启与关闭。视频将以Theora OGV格式保存在您用户目录下的Starcraft II Videos文件夹中。录制高质量视频可能会极大地影响您的游戏体验。 /// You can toggle in-game video recording by pressing CTRL-F11 while playing a game or watching a replay. Videos are stored in your user directory's StarCraft II Videos folder in Theora OGV format. Recording high quality video may considerably slow down your game experience.=8002
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/AudioQuality,<c val="ffffff">音频质量：</c><n/>提高音频质量将获得更高的音频保真度，但会使文件体积增大。 /// <c val="ffffff">Audio Quality:</c><n/>Increasing audio quality will provide greater audio fidelity at a cost of larger video files.=8003
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/FrameRate,<c val="ffffff">帧率：</c><n/>帧率指每秒录制的帧的数量。帧率越高，所录制出的视频越流畅，但会使视频文件体积增大。录制高帧率的视频可能会影响游戏运行速度。 /// <c val="ffffff">Framerate:</c><n/>Framerate refers to the number of frames recorded per second. A higher framerate will result in smoother video playback at a cost of larger video files. Recording at a higher framerate may slow down your game experience.=8004
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/RecordAudioCheckbox,<c val="ffffff">开启音频录制：</c><n/>录制视频时包含声音。 /// <c val="ffffff">Enable Audio:</c><n/>Enables recording audio with your video.=8005
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/RecordTriggers,<c val="ffffff">触发器录制：</c><n/>开启该选项将允许游戏根据创建地图时预先设定的条件自动触发视频的录制。玩家创建地图时可以添加“开始录制视频”触发器，使视频的录制更为方便。如果您不想在某些地图中自动录制视频，请保持该选项的禁用状态。 /// <c val="ffffff">Record From Triggers:</c><n/>Enabling this option will allow you to record video from in-game triggers. Players can create maps with "MovieStartRecording" triggers to facilitate the creation of movies. Keep this option off if you do not want videos to automatically record on certain maps.=8006
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/Resolution,<c val="ffffff">分辨率：</c><n/>该选项决定了录制视频采用的像素数量。较高的分辨率对应较好的画面质量，但会延长录制时间。要获得最佳效果，请使用与您的屏幕高宽比相匹配的分辨率。 /// <c val="ffffff">Resolution:</c><n/>Determines the size in pixels of the recorded video. Higher resolutions have much better image quality, but they are slower to record. For best results, use a resolution that matches your game's aspect ratio.=8007
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/SlowGame,<c val="ffffff">录制视频时游戏减速：</c><n/>该选项决定了录制视频时是否减慢游戏速度以弥补性能下降造成的影响。开启此选项可以带来更好的视频效果，但在多人游戏中无法开启此选项。禁用此选项时录制的视频将受到帧数下降的影响，但音频部分不会受到影响。 /// <c val="ffffff">Slow Game while Recording:</c><n/>Determines whether or not game time will slow down to adjust for the performance drop while recording video. This will result in better looking videos, but it cannot be used while participating in multiplayer games. Videos recorded with this option disabled will record the drop in framerate, but your audio will be unaffected.=8008
UI/VideoOptionsTooltips/VideoQuality,<c val="ffffff">视频质量：</c><n/>该选项决定了录制视频采用的压缩量。更高的视频质量会带来更好的画面质量，但会增加视频文件大小。 /// <c val="ffffff">Video Quality:</c><n/>Determines the amount of compression used when recording your video. Greater video quality will result in better image quality but much larger video files.=8009

This may cause distortion with USB headsets or microphones. Not all input devices support boost.=8032
UI/VoiceOptionsTooltips/MicrophoneHardware,<c val="ffffff">操作系统麦克风静音：</c><n/>切换麦克风在操作系统中的静音设置。<n/><n/><c val="ff0000">注意：该操作将影响麦克风在其它应用程序中的状态，退出《星际争霸II》后设置不会恢复。</c> /// <c val="ffffff">Mute OS Microphone:</c><n/>Toggles the OS microphone mute state.<n/><n/><c val="ff0000">Note: This will affect other applications and will remain in effect when StarCraft II is not running.</c>=8033
UI/VoiceOptionsTooltips/MicrophoneTest,<c val="ffffff">麦克风测试：</c><n/>切换麦克风测试。开启后，所有通过麦克风输入的语音都将以选定的语音输出设备进行回放。 /// <c val="ffffff">Microphone Test:</c><n/>Toggle the microphone test. While enabled, all voice spoken through the microphone will play back through the selected voice output device.=8034
UI/VoiceOptionsTooltips/MicrophoneVolume,<c val="ffffff">麦克风音量：</c><n/>该选项决定了麦克风声音输入的音量。如果其他玩家很难听到您的声音，则提高该项。如果设置了自动调节，则该选项会被禁用。 /// <c val="ffffff">Microphone Volume:</c><n/>Determines how loudly audio is recorded. Increase this if others have a hard time hearing you. Disabled if Auto setting is being used.=8035
UI/VoiceOptionsTooltips/Mode,<c val="ffffff">语音聊天模式：</c><n/>该选项决定了麦克风的激活方式。设定为语音激活时，麦克风会在出现语音时自动激活。设定为按键发言时则需要按下按键才能进行语音聊天。 /// <c val="ffffff">Voice Chat Mode:</c><n/>Determines how your microphone is activated. Voice Activated will automatically activate chat when you speak. Push-to-Talk requires you to hold a button while speaking.=8036
UI/VoiceOptionsTooltips/OutputDevice,<c val="ffffff">输出设备：</c><n/>选择用于播放聊天语音的扬声器或耳机。语音聊天设备可以不同于游戏设备。 /// <c val="ffffff">Output Device:</c><n/>Selects the speakers or headphones used to play back voice chat. Voice chat does not need to play through the same device as the game.=8037
UI/VoiceOptionsTooltips/PTTHotkey,<c val="ffffff">按键发言键：</c><n/>该选项决定了用于激活语音聊天的按键设置。按下该按钮，再按下要设为发言键的按键以修改当前的值。 /// <c val="ffffff">Push-to-Talk Key:</c><n/>Determines the key used to activate voice chat. Press the button then the key you want to use to change this value.=8038

LoadingScreen/Help00,按下<k val="AlertRecall"/>键可使镜头切换至最近发生的事件，如战斗警告或最新生成的单位。 /// Press<k val="AlertRecall"/> to center the camera on a recent event, such as a combat warning or a recently created unit.=12573
LoadingScreen/Help01,您可以通过按下<k val="ControlGroupAssign1"/>键对单位进行编组。按下<k val="ControlGroupRecall1"/>键便可以重新选中编组中的单位。 /// You can store a unit selection by pressing<k val="ControlGroupAssign1"/>. Press<k val="ControlGroupRecall1"/> to recall the selection.=12574
LoadingScreen/Help02,按下<k val="SubgroupNext"/>键可以在选中的单位中切换兵种，使单位技能的使用更为简单。 /// Press<k val="SubgroupNext"/> to cycle through different types of selected units, making it easier to use their abilities.=12575
LoadingScreen/Help03,位于高地上的单位在作战时不会遭到还击。命令单位移上斜坡或调遣空中单位都可以帮助您获得视野，对付高地上的敌人。 /// Units on higher ground can attack without endangering themselves. To counter this, gain vision of the attackers by running up ramps or bringing air units.=12576
LoadingScreen/Help04,萨尔纳加瞭望塔能够提供开阔的视野。将单位移至瞭望塔附近可将其激活。 /// Xel'Naga Towers provide vision across a large area. Stand a unit near a Xel'Naga Tower to control it.=12577
LoadingScreen/Help05,摧毁岩石可打通前往新区域的通道。 /// Rocks can be destroyed to open up new paths.=12578
LoadingScreen/Help06,起始区域的资源将迟早会消耗殆尽。向其它资源点扩张以保证稳定的收入。 /// Your starting area will eventually run out of resources. Expand to new resource locations to secure additional income.=12579
LoadingScreen/Help07,早期建立分基地进行扩张是一种冒险的举动，但额外的资源收入有时值得您去这样做。 /// Expanding to a new resource location early in a game is risky, but the extra income is sometimes worth the risk.=12580
LoadingScreen/Help08,武器和护甲升级会对现有及随后生产的单位产生影响，因此战斗持续越久，升级带来的受益便越多。 /// Weapon and armor upgrades affect existing and future units, so their benefits quickly add up over the course of longer games.=12581
LoadingScreen/Help09,持续生产SCV、探机或工蜂是推动经济发展的关键。 /// The key to a strong economy is constantly training SCVs, Probes, or Drones.=12582
LoadingScreen/Help10,为单个晶体矿簇分配的SCV、探机或工蜂的最佳数量为2个，瓦斯气泉则为3个。 /// It takes 2 SCVs, Probes, or Drones to optimally harvest a Mineral Field and 3 for a Vespene Geyser.=12583
LoadingScreen/Help11,利用编组功能，您在镜头不切换至基地的情况下便可以生产单位。 /// You can use control groups to train units without even looking at your base.=12584
LoadingScreen/Help12,您可以通过双击某个单位，或按住CTRL键并点击某个单位的方式选中附近所有同类型的单位。 /// You can select all nearby units of a given type by double-clicking on a unit, or by holding CTRL and clicking on a unit.=12585
LoadingScreen/Help13,高产矿脉晶体矿的颜色为黄色，对其进行采集的效率高于普通晶体矿脉。 /// Rich Mineral Fields are yellow, and can be harvested faster than normal Mineral Fields.=12586
LoadingScreen/Help14,摧毁所有敌人的建筑或最后一个离开游戏，才能获得一场多人游戏的胜利。 /// To win a multiplayer game, destroy all enemy structures or be the last player still in the game.=12587
LoadingScreen/Help15,成就是完成游戏中的各种目标后获得的在线奖励。进入个人资料页面可查看您可以获得的成就。 /// Achievements are online trophies for accomplishing various goals in the game. View your profile to see what achievements you can earn.=12588
LoadingScreen/Help16,武器描述中的“vs 重甲：5”表示该武器对重甲目标造成的伤害为5点。 /// Weapons that list damage as "vs Armored: 5" do a total of 5 damage to targets that are considered Armored.=12589
LoadingScreen/Help17,敌人在不借助侦测单位帮助的情况下无法攻击隐形或潜地的单位，铁鸦、侦测器或眼虫都属于侦测单位。 /// Cloaked or burrowed units cannot be attacked unless spotted by a detector, such as a Raven, Observer, or Overseer.=12590
LoadingScreen/Help18,侦测单位能够识别幻像，铁鸦、侦测器或眼虫都属于侦测单位。 /// Detectors like Ravens, Observers, and Overseers can spot the difference between Protoss Hallucinations and real units.=12591
LoadingScreen/Help19,如果您的系统连接了麦克风设备，则可以按下<k val="PTT"/>同盟友聊天。 /// If you have a microphone, you can hold down the<k val="PTT"/> key to talk to your allies.=12592
LoadingScreen/Help20,按下<k val="CameraFollow"/>键可使镜头跟随选中的单位。 /// Press<k val="CameraFollow"/> to have the game follow a selected unit as it moves across the battlefield.=12593
LoadingScreen/Help21,SCV能够修理受损的建筑或机械单位。参与修理的SCV越多，则修理的进度便越快。 /// SCVs can be used to repair buildings or mechanical units. The more SCVs repairing, the faster the repair is complete.=12594
LoadingScreen/Help22,在战斗中，使用一些SCV对关键性防御设施或作战单位进行修理以协助战斗。 /// Use several SCVs to keep vital defenses or combat units alive during a fight.=12595
LoadingScreen/Help23,使用医疗运输机配合大型步兵作战团队的战斗。利用其运输能力将步兵单位运送至敌后，展开奇袭。 /// Use Medivacs to support large infantry groups. Use their transport abilities to take infantry behind enemy lines for surprise attacks.=12596
LoadingScreen/Help24,恶火的火焰喷射器可对火力线覆盖的所有敌方单位造成伤害。靠近大批聚集的敌人后发动攻击，以使造成的伤害最大化。 /// Hellions do damage in a straight line with their flame thrower. Get close to packs of enemies to maximize your damage.=12597

Skin/Info/Adept,使徒是经受过高度训练的战场指挥官。他们使用净化者科技来增强自身的灵能潜力，可以投射自身的阴影然后实现远距离传送。 /// Highly trained battlefield commanders, adepts utilize Purifier technology to amplify their psionic potential. They are capable of projecting shades of themselves and teleporting across great distances.=16300
Skin/Info/AdeptCE,达拉姆的星空锻造厂虽然可以重构来自格拉修斯的各种净化者武器，但是其性能仍然无法媲美凯拉克斯的原型武器。 /// The Daelaam's starforges may be capable of reconstructing the Purifier ordnance from Glacius, but they have yet to match the optimal performance of Karax's original prototypes.=16301
Skin/Info/AdeptGolden,末日之战结束后，一股怀旧风潮开始在圣堂武士中间盛行。其中一些使徒身穿昔日的正统仪式铠甲，以此彰显心中不灭的骄傲。 /// Nostalgic sentiment has been growing among the templar after the End War. Some adepts show their pride by wearing formal ceremonial armor from bygone days. =16302
Skin/Info/AdeptIhanrii,即便是久经沙场的伊罕利使徒，在求救信号将他们从科普卢星区边缘世界的深度静滞状态中唤醒后，也需要时间来确定方位。 /// Even battle-hardened Ihan-rii adepts needed time to get their bearings after a distress signal woke them from deep stasis on the fringes of the Koprulu Sector.=16303
Skin/Info/AdeptPurifier,这些智能人格战士都经过了相位技师凯拉克斯的改良，已成为净化者大军的中坚力量。他们的灵敏与出色令人震撼。 /// Refined by Phase-smith Karax, these AI warriors have become central figures in Purifier armies, impressing all who see them with their agility and refinement.=16304
Skin/Info/AdeptTaldarim,尽管达拉姆使徒使用的灵能增幅科技刚被研发不久，但是已经被塔达林逆向工程破解，并且装备给了他们最优秀的战士。 /// Despite its recent development, the psionic amplification technology used by the Daelaam's adepts has already been reverse engineered by the Tal'darim and equipped on their most promising warriors.=16305
Skin/Info/Archon,执政官虽然拥有无可匹敌的灵能力量，但是为之而付出的代价也极其高昂。两名圣堂武士必须自我牺牲才能合为一体，而这充分体现了绝无仅有的大无畏献身精神。 /// Archons boast overwhelming psionic power, but it comes at a high cost. Two templar must sacrifice themselves for an archon to be formed, making each one an embodiment of unparalleled heroism.=16306
Skin/Info/Armory,军械库是围绕几个涡轮机建造的。在研究员们不知疲倦地改良泰伦战争器械的同时，这些设备能够确保建筑一直处于安全的温度范围内。 /// The armory is built around several turbines. These keep the building within temperature specifications while researchers work tirelessly to improve terran war machinery.=16307
Skin/Info/ArmoryCovertOps,帝国在精钢装甲技术上取得的最新突破源自于对特战队找到的萨尔纳加构造体进行了分子级解析。 /// The Dominion's latest advances in neosteel armor were developed through the molecular examination of xel'naga constructs recovered by special forces teams.=16308
Skin/Info/ArmorySilver,有报道称星灵闯入了泰拉多尔九号星的军械库，而这一行为被指控是间谍活动，尽管伊罕利的领导者坚称这些事件只是因为定居者误把这些闪闪发光的建筑当成了人类博物馆。 /// Reports of protoss wandering into Tyrador IX's armories led to accusations of espionage, though Ihan-rii leadership insisted that these incidents were the result of settlers mistaking the gleaming structures for terran museums.=16309
Skin/Info/Assimilator,即便是科技高度发达的星灵也喜欢在采集高能瓦斯领域不断创新。他们研发了多种吸纳舱来采集这一宝贵资源。 /// Even the highly advanced protoss appreciate the myriad applications of vespene gas. They developed assimilators to harvest this useful resource.=16310
Skin/Info/AssimilatorForged,塔达林吸纳舱贪婪地从地下抽取着高能瓦斯，引发的地震毁灭了周围的生态系统。 /// Tal'darim assimilators greedily wrench vespene gas from the ground, triggering earthquakes that decimate surrounding ecosystems.=16311
Skin/Info/AssimilatorIhanrii,伊罕利星灵认为他们自己非常慷慨，他们允许人类继续生存在他们古老而神圣的家园——阿拉基尔，更不用说还让人类在此开采高能瓦斯了。=16312

Skin/Info/Baneling,在卡斯克围城战中首次观察到的爆虫，是一种由跳虫进化而来的高度不稳定的爆炸性战斗变种。很少有材料能抵御它们爆炸时释放出的强酸烧蚀。 /// First observed during the Siege of Cask, the baneling is a highly volatile and explosive combat strain evolved from the zergling. Few materials can resist the acidic burst released upon their detonation.=16314
Skin/Info/BanelingMecha,重造爆虫对工程师们提出了一项特殊的难题，因为他们千辛万苦采集到的酸液囊会不断溶解周遭一切钢化结构。幸运的是，他们最终成功了。 /// The recreation of the baneling posed a unique problem for engineers, as their carefully harvested acid sacs kept melting through the surrounding plate infrastructure. Eventually, they made it work.=16315
Skin/Info/BanelingNest,异虫的巢群里必须要有一个爆虫巢穴来提供爆虫的基因代码。一旦筑巢完毕，战场上的任意一只跳虫就可以被命令在短时间内形成一个肉质的虫蛹，接着它们会以爆虫的形态破壳而出——变异成一种肮脏、臃肿的生物，其背部不停颤动着一团球状的、充满强酸的绿色囊泡。 /// The zerg hive cluster must have a baneling nest to add the baneling breed's genetic code. Once a nest is in place, any zergling on the field can be commanded to form a fleshy chrysalis for a brief pupation state, and then it will burst forth as a baneling--a foul, bloated creature with bulbous, acid-filled green sacs pulsating on its back.=16316
Skin/Info/BanelingNestMecha,仿生机械爆虫巢穴的上半部分是悬空的，其中运用了和泰伦战列巡航舰一样的反重力技术。 /// The upper half of the Simulant baneling nest is held aloft by the same antigravity technology deployed in terran battlecruisers.=16317
Skin/Info/BanelingNestRCZ,为了使人类的关键防御工事崩塌，塞伯鲁斯从幕后控制了爆虫巢穴，使其能够在遍布泰拉多尔九号星的洞穴网络中引爆。 /// To trigger the collapse of key terran fortifications, Cerberus baneling nests have been rigged to detonate in cave networks across Tyrador IX.=16318
Skin/Info/BanelingPrimal,在见识了凯瑞甘虫群中的爆虫后，德哈卡也鼓励自己的族群变异出了类似的变种。 /// Inspired by the banelings in Kerrigan's Swarm, Dehaka has encouraged the mutation of a similar strain of creatures within his pack.=16319
Skin/Info/BanelingRCZ,替换掉爆虫整个神经系统只是为了让它能够立即爆炸，做这种投资到底效果如何是值得怀疑的。幸运的是，塞伯鲁斯的客户们并不缺钱。 /// The return on investment for replacing a baneling's entire nervous system, only to have it immediately blow up, is dubious. Luckily, Cerberus's clients have quite a lot of money to spend.=16320
Skin/Info/BanelingWebby,浑身长满脊刺的利维坦虫巢跳虫至今保留着它们爆虫的酸液囊。即便是彻底的变异也无法改变它们核心精华中的混乱天性。 /// The spine-like growths of Leviathan Brood zerglings remain present on the acid sacs of their banelings. Even a total metamorphosis is incapable of changing the chaotic nature of their core essence.=16321
Skin/Info/Banshee,普罗希昂工业集团对女妖的定位是经济实用型战机。专门为前线步兵提供空中支援而建造，它们是执行战术打击的理想飞行器。 /// Procyon Industries designed banshees to be both economical and effective. Built specifically to provide air support for frontline infantry, they are ideal aircraft for tactical strikes.=16322
Skin/Info/BansheeCovertOps,帝国工程师们对女妖的两台VTOL涡扇进行了重大升级，在机体尾部加装新的垂直稳定装置后，战机的稳定性和飞行性能得到了极大改善。 /// Dominion engineers have made critical upgrades in the banshee's twin VTOL turbofans, enabling superior stability and performance when paired with the new vertical stabilizer in the rear of the craft.=16323

Skin/Info/BroodLordPrimal,原始异虫族群吸收了少量的巢虫领主，由此诞生了一种完全不同的生物，拥有不同寻常的利爪。 /// A small number of brood lords have been integrated into primal zerg packs, resulting in a strikingly different creature most notable for its unusual claws.=16338

Skin/Info/Colossus,巨像是星灵设计的第一种专注于毁灭的机器人。它们昭示了一段血腥的历史，也用实力确保了和平的未来。 /// Colossi were the first protoss robots designed solely for destruction. They are both a symbol of a bloody history and a necessary weapon to secure a peaceful future.=16352

Skin/Info/ColossusGolden,一批经历了末日之战的巨像，在经过精挑细选后，被使用最顶级的材料重新改造成了传统样式。如今的它们成为了古代星灵机器人技术的集大成者。 /// Selected colossi that saw combat in the End War have been remodeled in a traditionalist style using the finest materials available. They now resemble the grandest of ancient protoss robotics.=16354
Skin/Info/ColossusIhanrii,伊罕利巨像的大量陨石组件，都是经由重新调校后的萨尔那加动能机所散发出的虚空能量，将它们悬浮托举并聚拢在一起。 /// The many stone components of the Ihan-rii colossus are levitated and held together by void energies emanated from repurposed xel'naga dynamos.=16355
Skin/Info/ColossusPurifier,净化者在工程学上的最新成果催生出了一种线条流畅、工艺精细的加强版巨像，简直就是一台战争机器艺术品。 /// The latest in Purifier engineering has yielded a sleek, subtly enhanced colossus that is nonetheless a brutal war machine.=16356
Skin/Info/ColossusTal,圣物大战早已结束，被掩埋和遗忘在星区各处旧战场上的巨像，经常被追求更强火力的塔达林晋升者挖掘出来，重新投入使用。 /// Relics of wars long over, colossi that lay buried and forgotten across the sector are often unearthed and reactivated by Tal'darim ascendants who seek superior firepower.=16357
Skin/Info/ColossusTaldarim,低阶的晋升者们经常挑战对方去关闭并控制一台激活的巨像。如果成功，那么塔达林就多了一个强大的战争机器；如果失败，则少了一个升格对手。 /// Lower ranking ascendants often dare each other to disable and commandeer an active colossus. If one succeeds, the Tal'darim gain a powerful war machine. If not, a rival ascendant has been eliminated.=16358
Skin/Info/CommandCenter,既能移动部署而且功能实用的指挥中心是资源处理中心，它们可以迁移到任何晶体矿或高能瓦斯丰富的地点。 /// Mobile and practical, command centers are resource processors that can relocate to wherever minerals or vespene gas are plentiful.=16359
Skin/Info/CommandCenterCovertOps,加固后的反推器着陆架能让这种指挥中心即便是在最严酷的环境中也能找到安全的落脚点。 /// Reinforced repulsor landing claws help this command center find solid footing in even the harshest environments.=16360
Skin/Info/CommandCenterRemastered,早期迭代版本的指挥中心有一个可扩展的接口，以便与外部附件连接。后来为了提高安全性，内部操作台取代了这种接口。 /// Previous iterations of the command center had an extensible interface in order to connect with external add-ons. These were later replaced with internal bays for increased security.=16361
Skin/Info/CommandCenterSilver,在伊罕利星灵抵达后，泰拉多尔的指挥中心接待了来自科普卢星区各处的外交使节。每名使节都想要拉拢这些新来的人，来达成自己的政治目的。 /// After the arrival of the Ihan-rii protoss, Tyrador's command centers played host to diplomatic envoys from around the Koprulu Sector, each intent on recruiting the newcomers to their own specific political agenda.=16362
Skin/Info/Corruptor,靠生物制造出的电磁场而漂浮起来的腐化者，可以喷洒具有超强腐蚀性的强酸液体，即便是最牢固的建造材料也无法抵御侵蚀。 /// Held aloft by a biologically produced electromagnetic field, corruptors can spray a stream of caustic acid that eats through even the most durable of construction materials.=16363
Skin/Info/CorruptorMecha,与孵生孢子不同，这些机械腐化者拥有自我修复能力的纳米机器人，它们被编程后可以产生与孢子相同的功能，就这一点足以让人不安了。 /// Rather than spores, these mechanical corruptors possess self-replicating nanites that have been programmed to perform the same function, disturbingly enough.=16364
Skin/Info/CorruptorPrimal,最早的腐化者具有虫群和原始异虫两种特征。后者进化出了更粗的利爪和更厚的甲壳，以更好地辅助其严格的进食过程。 /// The original corruptors have the distinction of being adapted by both the Swarm and the primal zerg. The latter have adapted thicker claws and carapaces to assist with their rigorous feeding process.=16365
Skin/Info/CorruptorRCZ,阿克图尔斯·蒙斯克倒台后，被迫转入地下的“塞伯鲁斯工程”逐步为他们的神经重新编程计划确立了新的方向，对象不再是泰伦士兵而是异虫。 /// Driven underground after the fall of Arcturus Mengsk, the Cerberus Program evolved their neural reprogramming initiative, targeting zerg instead of terran soldiers.=16366
Skin/Info/CorruptorWebby,虽然坚硬的脊刺和蹼状特征经常透露出它们的水栖背景，但是利维坦虫巢的腐化者们还是成功适应了在超重环境中生存。 /// While hardened spines and webbed features often suggest an aquatic background, the Leviathan Brood's corruptors adapted them to survive in high gravity environments.=16367
Skin/Info/CreepTumorMecha,这些由叛变仿生机械虫后制造的菌毯肿瘤，必定藏有复杂的纳米科技秘辛，但是想做进一步调查的尝试总会被肿瘤结构受损即自爆的防御机制所破坏。 /// Sophisticated nanotechnology must lie at the heart of creep tumors created by rogue Simulant queens, though further investigation has been stymied by the tumors' tendency to detonate when cut open.=16368
Skin/Info/CyberneticsCore,星灵被外界所熟知的一点是，他们会给倒下的战士们加装人造躯体，赋予他们第二次生命，以重获战斗的荣光。控制芯核在研发此项科技的过程中起到了关键性的作用。 /// The protoss are known to pair elite fallen warriors with artificial bodies, granting them a second life in glorious combat. The cybernetics core plays a large role in developing this technology.=16369
Skin/Info/CyberneticsCoreForged,所有控制芯核都具备将生物体植入精密器械的能力，但是塔达林的控制芯核有一点不同，那就是整个过程会非常痛苦。 /// All cybernetics cores possess the ability to bind biological beings to elaborate machinery; in Tal'darim cybernetics cores, the main difference is that the process is unimaginably painful.=16370
Skin/Info/CyberneticsCoreIhanrii,人类在侦查伊罕利定居点的过程中，发现了一种和当代星灵控制芯核非常类似的构造体，不过这种伊罕利构造体散发出的能量完全不同。=16371
Skin/Info/Cyclone,原本是设计成全自动控制的高机动性战车，后来还是重新设计为有人驾驶。毕竟，人类驾驶员具有高度的不可预知性。 /// Originally intended to be fully automated, this mobile assault vehicle was redesigned to accommodate a pilot. After all, nothing can match the unpredictability of a human driver.=16372
Skin/Info/CycloneCovertOps,为了提高在特种作战任务中的机动性，这种战车经历了大幅度的重新设计，其中包括能更容易跨越困难地形和狭小空间的外露式履带。 /// This vehicle has undergone extensive redesigns to increase its maneuverability in special forces missions, including exposed treads that will cross difficult terran and small spaces more readily.=16373
Skin/Info/CycloneJunker,米拉的雇佣兵们大幅强化了他们的飓风，加装了额外的钢板和大量的尖刺。不过，由于工艺上的不严谨，这样的改装丝毫没有改善吸收伤害的能力。 /// Mira's mercs have significantly bulked up their cyclones, adding extra plating and a generous number of spikes. However, due to their hasty engineering, its ability to absorb damage remains the same.=16374
Skin/Info/CycloneSilver,当塞伯鲁斯异虫袭击泰拉多尔九号星时，一些被派去防御的飓风战车装备的仍然是供夜间游乐园表演使用的毫无杀伤力的烟花。 /// When the Cerberus zerg attacked Tyrador IX, a few cyclones sent to defend were still armed with harmless fireworks used for nightly amusement park displays.=16375
Skin/Info/CycloneUmojan,如果模仿是最高形式的奉承，那么这些飓风就是尤摩扬工程师对泰伦帝国独创性的由衷赞赏。 /// If imitation is the sincerest form of flattery, then these cyclones are the Umojan engineers' elaborate tribute to the ingenuity of the Terran Dominion.=16376
Skin/Info/DarkShrine,黑暗圣坛曾是奈拉齐姆独立社会的象征性丰碑。在回归卡莱社会后，奈拉齐姆将其重新作为黑暗圣堂武士的训练场。 /// The dark shrine once stood as a monument to the independent society of the Nerazim. After the rejoining the khalai, the Nerazim repurposed it as a training ground for dark templar.=16377
Skin/Info/DarkShrineForged,鲜血猎手是高阶领主恶毒意志的执行者，除了他们没有人知道在塔达林的黑暗圣坛里到底发生了什么。 /// None but the blood hunters, enforcers of the Highlords' malevolent will, know what transpires within the Tal'darim dark shrine.=16378
Skin/Info/DarkShrineIhanrii,伊罕利黑暗圣坛的顶部冒着滚烫的烟雾，这说明圣坛内部的温度极高，尽管人类的热学分析显示这些可变形陨石外部的温度已接近冰点。 /// The superheated fumes venting from the top of the Ihan-rii dark shrine suggest infernal internal temperatures, though terran thermal analysis indicates the animated stone exterior is near-freezing.=16379
Skin/Info/DarkTemplar,身为强大的奈拉齐姆灵能战士，黑暗圣堂武士了解如何操控虚空的力量。他们从阴影中出击，致命且无情。 /// Powerful psionic warriors of the Nerazim, dark templar have learned how to manipulate the powers of the Void. They strike from the shadows, deadly and relentless.=16380

Skin/Info/DarkTemplarIhanrii,在早年训练中，伊罕利星灵都会被绑上一块能与他们灵能特征产生谐鸣的虚空水晶。当他们成年后，这块水晶早已被磨得像一枚矛尖一样致命锋利。 /// Early in their training, Ihan-rii protoss are bound to a void crystal that resonates with their unique psionic signature. Once they reach adulthood, this crystal is sharpened into a deadly spearpoint.=16382
Skin/Info/DarkTemplarPurifier,在与奈拉齐姆联系日益紧密后，净化者在警戒者的基础上设计了一种可以模仿黑暗圣堂武士战斗技艺的全新变体。 /// After increased interaction with the Nerazim, the Purifiers have designed a new variant on the sentinel that mimics the combat prowess of Dark Templar warriors.=16383
Skin/Info/DarkTemplarTaldarim,塔达林整个社会残忍无情。那些被认为太弱小而不配为高阶领主效命的弱者都将遭到残酷捕杀，负责处决他们的正是那些行走在阴影中的鲜血猎手。 /// Tal'darim society is brutal and unforgiving. Those deemed too weak to be of service to their Highlord are ruthlessly hunted down and executed by the blood hunters, who stalk their prey unseen.=16384
Skin/Info/Disruptor,最初作为净化者项目一部分研发而来的干扰者，是星灵最具有致命性武器中的一种。它们的太阳能武库破坏力惊人。 /// Originally developed as part of the Purifier program, disruptors are among the deadliest of protoss armaments. Their solarite arsenal is capable of immense devastation.=16385
Skin/Info/DisruptorGolden,和巨像的情况类似，经历了末日之战的干扰者也被重新改造，它们成为了星灵伟大胜利的不朽纪念。也许随着时间的流逝，星灵的苦难回忆才会终将淡去。 /// Much like the colossi, disruptors that saw combat in the End War have been refurbished as reminders of the protoss' moments of victory. Perhaps with time, the memories of their losses will fade.=16386
Skin/Info/DisruptorIhanrii,伊罕利干扰者直接从它们的主力战舰的水晶核心中提取劈啪作响的绿色能源。任何不小心触碰到中央能源管路的生物体都会被瞬间蒸发。 /// Ihan-rii disruptors draw crackling green energy directly from the crystal cores of their capital ships. Anything biological that makes contact with the central power conduit is promptly vaporized.=16387
Skin/Info/DisruptorPurifier,塞布罗斯号生产的干扰者配备了高级板甲与协议优化，两者一同体现了净化者在最新技术上持之以恒的研究与投入。 /// The latest disruptors from Cybros feature advanced plating and protocol refinements that reflect their investment in ongoing research.=16388
Skin/Info/DisruptorTaldarim,虽然塔达林经常鄙夷达拉姆对武器的选择，但是他们很快就夺取并重新改装了大量的干扰者。这种毁灭性的力量实在是令他们难以无动于衷。 /// The Tal'darim often scoff at the Daelaam's choice of weaponry, but they were quick to seize and repurpose as many disruptors as they could. Such destructive power is too great to ignore.=16389
Skin/Info/Drone,心智单一且劳作勤恳的工蜂，其体内携带的基因代码可以变异成所有种类的异虫建筑。它们只需要资源和菌毯来滋养不断裂生的生物质。 /// Single-minded and diligent, drones hold within their genetic code the evolutionary potential of all zerg structures. All they require are resources and creep to nourish their added biomass.=16390
Skin/Info/DroneBlizzcon17,这只奇异的工蜂诞生于一片锈蚀的人类废墟，但这并没有影响它的成长，为了适应环境，它的血肉已经与碎石融为一体。 /// This unusual drone hatched amid a pile of rusting terran wreckage. Rather than suffering from the interference, its flesh adapted to fuse itself to the rubble.=16391
Skin/Info/DroneMecha,仿生工程最先建造的这些机械工蜂，原本是用来在打靶练习中测试战斗技法和武器威力，但是没过多久它们变得更大了。 /// The Simulant Project began with the construction of a mechanical drone that could be used during target practice to test alternate combat techniques and weapons, but it soon grew much larger.=16392
Skin/Info/DronePrimal,原始工蜂随时随地都有性命之忧，因为它们族群中更强大的成员们每当需要额外的营养时，就会拿它们当零食。 /// Primal drones often find themselves in a perilous position, as stronger members of their packs have been known to feed on them when they require additional nourishment.=16393
Skin/Info/DroneRCZ,和塞伯鲁斯异虫的其它成员一样，塞伯鲁斯工蜂的神经系统也用神经机械科技进行了替代，使其可以完全操控机械骨骼。 /// Like the rest of the Cerberus zerg, this drone's nervous system has been replaced with cybernetic technology, enabling full musculoskeletal control.=16394
Skin/Info/DroneRemastered,较早期进化版本的工蜂不仅色彩特别鲜艳，而且各项反应动作更具攻击性。只是这一变种在接下来的时间里逐渐消失在了种类庞杂的虫群之中。=16395
Skin/Info/DroneWebby,充满剧毒的鳍条是一种常见的防御机制，旨在吓阻掠食者。一些生物仅仅靠模仿这种可怕的外形来赶走不速之扰。 /// Poisonous fin rays are a universal defense mechanism signaling predators to stay away. Some creatures merely mimic their deadly appearance to discourage unwanted aggression.=16396
Skin/Info/EngineeringBay,母巢之战结束后，泰伦人大力发展了他们的工程能力。正因为人员的增加和工作复杂性的大幅度提升，工程站也失去了飞行能力。 /// The terrans heavily developed their engineering capabilities after the Brood War. Due to the increase in personnel and the intricacy of their work, the engineering bay is no longer cleared for flight.=16397
Skin/Info/EngineeringBayCovertOps,实验性工程站通过将AI程序置入模拟战场中进行对抗，进而提升研发速度。 /// Experimental engineering bays increase research speed by pitting rival AIs against one another in simulated battle.=16398
Skin/Info/EngineeringBaySilver,每座泰拉多尔骑士团的工程站或多或少都有致力于建造新的游乐场，尽管这项政策后来因塞伯鲁斯异虫的袭击而被暂停。 /// A portion of each Knights of Tyrador engineering bay is devoted to concocting new amusement park attractions, though this policy has been temporarily suspended in wake of the Cerberus zerg assault.=16399
Skin/Info/EvolutionChamber,无数的基因序列在进化腔内分割合并，不断为异虫大军产生出更加优异的基因。 /// Genetic sequences twist and merge within the evolution chamber, generating improvements to the zerg army. =16400
Skin/Info/EvolutionChamberMecha,和其它仿生机械建筑一样，进化腔也是由聚合物合金材料制造而成。这种金属具有很强的柔软性，可以适应进化腔内部发生的生物与机械的搅合过程。 /// Like other Simulant structures, the evolution chamber is constructed from a polymeric alloy capable of flexing to accommodate the roiling biomechanical processes within.=16401
Skin/Info/EvolutionChamberRCZ,在塞伯鲁斯的生物工程部门经历了好几个月的挫折之后，他们发现用指令信息素注满进化腔的动脉，可以控制这种结构过度进化的倾向。 /// After months of frustration in the Cerberus bioengineering department, it was discovered that pumping an evolution chamber's arteries full of command pheromones could just about tame the structure's hyperadaptive tendencies.=16402
Skin/Info/Extractor,这是一种生物建筑，它可以消化高能瓦斯，然后再将其排泄到小型的肉囊中。这些肉囊被完美地设计成可以由工蜂轻易地运送。 /// This is a biological structure that digests vespene gas before excreting it in small flesh sacs. These sacs are perfectly designed to be easily transportable by a drone.=16403
Skin/Info/ExtractorMecha,规划文档表明仿生工程的萃取房原本只是做装饰用。至于它们到底何时获得了生产高能瓦斯的能力，这还是一个迷。 /// Planning documents indicate that the Simulant Project's extractors were intended to be purely decorative. It remains unclear when they shifted into full vespene production.=16404
Skin/Info/ExtractorRCZ,塞伯鲁斯萃取房在泰拉多尔九号星的地下无止境地发出脉冲，从这个星球的地壳中榨取每一丝高能瓦斯，为进一步扩张提供动力。 /// Cerberus extractors pulse unremittingly beneath Tyrador IX's surface, leeching every trace of vespene gas from the planet's crust to power further expansion.=16405
Skin/Info/Factory,第二次全面战争期间，重工厂里的公厕被移除了。省出来的这块额外空间使得机械师们可以让攻城坦克在出厂前就已安装好攻城套件。 /// During the Second Great War, latrines were removed from factories. This extra space allowed mechanics to deploy siege tanks with siege capabilities already installed.=16406
Skin/Info/FactoryCovertOps,R36系列重工厂具有更坚固的起吊锚、加固型底座以及防弹涂层。 /// The R36-series factory features sturdier anchors, a reinforced foundation, and bulletproof coat of paint.=16407
Skin/Info/FactorySilver,好几座处于争议地区的人类工厂发生了不明原因的爆炸，只留下了闪闪发光的绿色陨石坑。这导致伊罕利星灵与泰拉多尔九号星领导者之间的谈判陷入了僵局。 /// Settlement negotiations between the Ihan-rii protoss and Tyrador IX's leaders hit a snag when several terran factories in a disputed area mysteriously exploded, leaving glowing green craters.=16408
Skin/Info/FleetBeacon,舰队航标负责强化附近星门与灵能矩阵之间的联系，从而使得巨型主力战舰可以折跃传送。 /// Fleet beacons serve to strengthen the connection of any nearby stargate to the psionic matrix, enabling the warp transport of massive capital ships.=16409
Skin/Info/FleetBeaconForged,塔达林的舰队航标强迫一股量级相当危险的灵能能量从其球体中心穿过，进而获得传送巨型战舰的能力。 /// The Tal'darim fleet beacon forces an almost certainly inadvisable amount of psionic energy through its central sphere, enabling the teleportation of massive and heavily armored warships.=16410
Skin/Info/FleetBeaconIhanrii,最终回到阿拉基尔的伊罕利建造了强大的舰队航标，以此在无垠的太空中寻找他们古老文明的幸存者。=16411
Skin/Info/FleetBeaconTaldarim,=16412
Skin/Info/Forge,锻炉为相位技师们提供了工作场所，供他们孜孜不倦地提升同胞们的武器、护甲和战舰性能。这些精英工程师们在艾尔得到光复前誓不言休。 /// The forge houses phase-smiths working tirelessly to improve the weapons, armor, and ships of their brethren. These elite engineers will not rest until the day Aiur is reclaimed.=16413
Skin/Info/ForgeForged,在塔达林锻炉中，被俘虏的卡莱工程师们遭受刑讯，被迫说出他们的科技秘密。 /// Inside Tal'darim forges, captured Khalai engineers are interrogated for their technological secrets. =16414

Skin/Info/FusionCore,聚变芯体中的工作是极其精细的。这里的研究员们利用反物质和核能来提高战列巡航舰的能力。 /// The work undertaken in the fusion core is extremely delicate. Researchers here harness antimatter and nuclear power to increase battlecruiser capability.=16417
Skin/Info/FusionCoreCovertOps,为了能完全满足新一代摩伊拉级战列巡航舰的需求，聚变芯体的能量输出提高了整整四倍，而且还不会增加其红热特征。 /// To accommodate the new Moirai-class battlecruiser, the fusion core's energy output was quadrupled without increasing its heat signature.=16418
Skin/Info/FusionCoreSilver,除了为轨道中的战列巡航舰提供支持外，液冷聚变芯体还为泰拉多尔九号星上的赌场、水上公园和全自动按摩院提供了大部分能源。 /// In addition to supporting the orbital battlecruiser fleet, liquid-cooled fusion cores provide most of the power for Tyrador IX's casinos, water parks, and robotic massage parlors.=16419
Skin/Info/Gateway,母巢之战结束后，星灵对萨尔纳加古代折跃科技进行了逆向研究。传送门现在可以在数秒内将战士传送到遥远的战场。 /// Following the Brood War, the protoss reverse engineered the ancient warp technology of the xel'naga. Gateways can now transport warriors to distant battlefields within seconds.=16420
Skin/Info/GatewayForged,塔达林传送门的折跃距离远远超出其卡莱竞品。然而这一优势也同样存在风险，那就是传送物有一定几率在折跃过程中被撕成碎片。 /// The Tal'darim gateway can warp warriors from much further away than its Khalai counterparts. One downside of the additional power is that passengers are occasionally torn to bits en route.=16421

Skin/Info/InfestorMecha,科研人员尝试制造AI程序的努力失败了，无法正常复制出感染者的神经寄生虫。当他们准备将感染者从生产品种中剔除时，令人意想不到的是，寄生虫的AI程序突然完美起效了…… /// Researchers failed to create an AI that replicated the infestors' neural parasites. They were removing the infestors from production when, unexpectedly, the parasites' AI began functioning perfectly...=16471
Skin/Info/InfestorPrimal,由于经常成为族群中其它更大更强竞争者的目标，感染者在它们的背部进化出了厚重的甲壳来保护自己。 /// As frequent targets of larger, more vicious competitors within their pack, primal infestors have evolved thickened plating along their back to protect themselves. =16472
Skin/Info/InfestorRCZ,为了满足一个重要企业客户的需求，塞伯鲁斯给出了名脆弱的感染者植入了支援性钛合金支架。 /// In response to feedback from an important corporate client, Cerberus implanted the notoriously fragile infestor with supportive titanium infrastructure.=16473
Skin/Info/InfestorWebby,感染者是一种菌落型生物，构成其主母虫的生物组织具有多种不同的用途。在利维坦感染者中，主母虫的防御性生物结构显得尤为明显。 /// As a colony creature, the organisms comprising the borboru matriarch took many different functions. Within Leviathan infestors, the defensive structures of the base creature are more pronounced.=16474
Skin/Info/LairMecha,当首个仿生工程孵化场变异成了虫穴后，项目组立刻展开了一次内部审计，不过负责工程师再也没找到过。 /// When the first Simulant Project hatchery mutated into a lair, an internal audit was launched, though the engineer responsible was never discovered.=16475
Skin/Info/Larva,这种不起眼的像蛆一样的生物包裹着一层看似很结实的皮层。它们可以变异成任何一种可怕的异虫生物。 /// This unassuming, maggot-like organism is covered in an deceptively strong hide and capable of mutating into any number of horrors.=16476
Skin/Info/LarvaMecha,仿生机械造物的视觉辨识度是创造机械幼虫时的一个重要考量，它们必须在外形和步态上做到与仿制对象极其相似。不过，这并不能完全解释为什么仿生工程的工程师们认为有必要复制异虫幼虫的标志性嘎吱噪音。 /// Visual recognition among Simulants is a common justification for creating mecha larvae that resemble their inspirations in silhouette and gait. Skin/Info/LarvaRCZ,塞伯鲁斯投入了大量的精力，将独特的刺激物映射到他们下令产生蜕变的幼虫之中，这种刺激物往往会造成巨大的痛苦。 /// Cerberus invested a great deal of effort in mapping unique and often painful stimuli to the metamorphoses of the zerg larva in which they resulted.=16478
Skin/Info/Liberator,在UED女武神战机的启发下，解放者的设计初衷原本是为了反制空中威胁。在加装空对地火炮之后，它们也能对付地表的敌方部队。 /// Inspired by the UED’s valkyries, liberators were originally designed to combat aerial threats. The addition of air-to-ground artillery allows them to also deal with terrestrial enemy forces.=16479
Skin/Info/LiberatorCovertOps,精钢建造工艺的最新技术提升催生了更加复杂的钢板设计，进而增强了解放者的变形过程，也由此招致了整个帝国舰队的嫉妒。 /// Recent improvements in neosteel construction have led to more complex plating designs that augment the liberator's transformation process, making it the envy of the Dominion fleet.=16480
Skin/Info/LiberatorJunker,米拉·汉的所有解放者全都是在一次剧情离奇的扑克游戏中赢来的。可惜，这些战舰不久之后全被她赔在了一个雇佣兵仇敌的手上。 /// Mira Han won all of her liberators in just one incredibly dramatic poker game. Unfortunately, she lost them all to a rival mercenary just a short time later.=16481
Skin/Info/LiberatorSilver,泰拉多尔九号星上的解放者配备了大量的前置泛光灯，这为它们在夜间巡视这颗星球壮美的景色时提供了良好的能见度。 /// Liberators on Tyrador IX are equipped with numerous front-facing floodlights, increasing visibility during late-night patrols of the planet's stunning wilderness. =16482
Skin/Info/LiberatorUmojan,只花了数年时间，尤摩扬护国军就推出了自己的解放者版本。其完全推倒重来的后推进器设计，引来了泰伦帝国工程师们嫉妒的目光。 /// It only took a few years for the Umojan Protectorate to unleash its version of the famous Liberator. Its wholly re-imagined rear thrusters have become the envy of the Terran Dominion engineering team.=16483
Skin/Info/Lurker,潜伏者一度被认为是灭绝了，直到它们的基因序列重新在一处野生巢群中找到。如今，潜伏者再次为虫群效力，从黑暗的地表之下刺杀敌人。 /// The lurker was believed lost until its sequences were recovered from a feral hive cluster. Now, the lurkers serve the Swarm once again, annihilating their foes from the darkness below.=16484
Skin/Info/LurkerDen,从远处看去，潜伏者巢穴仿佛是用一堆骨头而非肉做成的。凑近再看，原来它的外表更像是一层有着凹槽形状的厚皮革。 /// From a distance, the lurker den appears to be more bone than flesh. Upon closer inspection, the exterior is more like a grooved, thick leather.=16485
Skin/Info/LurkerDenMecha,在锻造纳米尖的潜伏者脊刺的过程中会产生巨大的热量，仿生机械潜伏者巢穴通过一个由排气孔和散热鳍片组成的复杂网络将热量排出。 /// The process of forging nano-tipped lurker spines generates tremendous heat, which the Simulant lurker den dissipates through a convoluted network of vents and cooling fins.=16486
Skin/Info/LurkerDenRCZ,塞伯鲁斯预料到他们需要提前进行侦察并设置一种隐形的前线防御措施，因此他们制造了大量的潜伏者巢穴来给他们侵扰泰拉多尔九号星的行动提供支持。 /// Anticipating the need for advance lookouts and a stealthy first line of defense, Cerberus produced an abundance of lurker dens to support their infestation of Tyrador IX.=16487
Skin/Info/LurkerMecha,大量的地下实验产生了一种功能强悍的机械潜伏者，只是它的尖刺被重新改变了形状，现在能在钝力冲撞下表现得更好。 /// Extensive subterranean tests yielded a capable mechanized lurker, aside from its spikes, which were reshaped to better perform under blunt force impact.=16488
Skin/Info/LurkerPrimal,一部分原始刺蛇进行了多次变异，并由此逐渐呈现出大量的潜伏者特征。如今它们长得跟潜伏者别无二致，几乎丧失了其刺蛇先祖的所有特点。 /// Some of the primal hydralisks developed mutations that led them to exhibit an increasing number of lurker characteristics. At this point, they resemble lurkers more than their hydralisk ancestors.=16489
Skin/Info/LurkerRCZ,一队被派去调查泰拉多尔九号星地表的伊罕利星灵，被恰好潜伏在着陆点的塞伯鲁斯潜伏者杀害。 /// A company of Ihan-rii protoss dispatched to investigate the surface of Tyrador IX were  massacred by Cerberus lurkers that happened to be burrowed at the landing site.=16490
Skin/Info/LurkerWebby,利维坦虫巢中的刺蛇与潜伏者的天然内在关系，在整个虫群中都找不出第二对。正因为如此，它们的变异能产生出大量额外的震地脊刺。 /// The innate connection between hydralisks and lurkers within the Leviathan Brood is unparalleled among the Swarm. As such, their metamorphosis yields a considerable number of additional seismic spines.=16491
Skin/Info/Marauder,劫掠者是步行坦克，是帝国设计用于针对异虫硬化甲壳的兵种。他们的榴弹在对付其它各种目标时一样有效。 /// Marauders are walking tanks, designed by the Dominion to combat the hardened carapaces of the zerg. Their grenades are effective against a variety of other targets, as well.=16492
Skin/Info/MarauderCovertOps,当帝国特战队就改良劫掠者作战服征询军队内部意见时，几乎所有人都只有一个要求——更粗的枪管。武器研究者们欣然地满足了大家。 /// When the Dominion Special Forces surveyed their personnel for improvements on marauder suits, only one dominated the conversation--bigger guns. The weapons researchers gladly obliged.=16493
Skin/Info/MarauderDeluxe,CMC-660型战斗装甲的最新改良方案已获批准，可以进行自愿者实战测试了。幸运的是，部队里有大量的劫掠者可以享受这一好处。=16494
Skin/Info/MarauderJunker,作为米拉·汉最初的一批手下，这些劫掠者与圈子里的其他雇佣兵们比起来算是挺忠诚了……不过这跟汉特别擅长玩敲诈和勒索也有关系。 /// As some of the original members of Mira Han's crew, these marauders are unusually loyal compared to others in the mercenary world... or Han just has exceptionally compelling blackmail on them.=16495
Skin/Info/MarauderSilver,泰拉多尔掠夺者的重量几乎是帝国标准的两倍。工程师们用增强的液压器和排气系统来补偿额外的密度。 /// The Tyrador marauder weighs almost twice the Dominion standard. Engineers compensated for the extra density with enhanced hydraulics and exhaust.=16496
Skin/Info/MarauderUmojan,CMC战斗装甲获得的多项特殊改进，为这些劫掠者提供了强化版的夜视能力，包括一个大幅度加固后的上半身框架，以支撑更重的榴弹发射器。 /// Special advancements in CMC armor have given these marauders improved night vision options, as well as a heavily reinforced upper frame to support their weightier grenade launchers. =16497
Skin/Info/Marine,有泰伦人的地方，就有陆战队员。他们当中有罪犯、叛乱分子，还有爱国者等等，他们随时随地都做好了战斗的准备。 /// Marines are the first line of defense for terran worlds across the sector. Comprised of convicts, rebels and patriots alike, they're always ready for a fight.=16498
Skin/Info/MarineCovertOps,虽然帝国特战队的服役期一般都不长，但是所有陆战队员都同意这份工作从来没有闲的时候。 /// One's service in the Dominion Special Forces may not always last long, but all marines can agree that there's never a dull moment on the job.=16499
Skin/Info/MarineJunker,那些爱问为什么这些雇佣喜欢带刀子的人显然是没见过他们在死水基地的酒吧里闹事的一幕。 /// Those who ask why these mercenaries carry bladed weapons have clearly never been in a backwater bar fight with them.=16500
Skin/Info/MarineRemastered,曾在母巢之战期间作战过的陆战队员们经常怀念起他们那时所穿的护甲，在他们眼里，当年的护甲穿起来要舒服得多。 /// Marines who fought in the Brood War often express nostalgia for the armor they wore back then, which they claim was significantly more comfortable.=16501
Skin/Info/MarineSilver,守卫泰拉多尔度假胜地和海滩的雇佣兵大多是白发苍苍的退伍军人，他们都是冲着工作轻松和薪水丰厚的承诺而来的。 /// The mercenary marines who guard Tyrador's resorts and beaches are mostly grizzled veterans lured to the system by the promise of an easy gig and generous pay.=16502
Skin/Info/MarineUmojan,尤摩扬陆战队员近期得到了一次令人激动的护甲升级，大幅度提高了新兵的安全性和平均部署时间，但这很有可能是在为未来的冲突进行备战。 /// Umojan marines have recently seen exciting armor upgrades—officially to increase the safety and average deployment time of recruits, but possibly as preparation for a future conflict.=16503
Skin/Info/MarineXPR,虽然战地豪猪给人的印象不是重度酒精患者就是酒吧闹事分子，但是这群佣兵在整个星区中的专业与实力无可挑剔。 /// Despite their reputation as heavy drinkers and barroom brawlers, the War Pigs are some of the most dependable mercenaries in the sector.=16504
Skin/Info/Medivac,既可以作为运输机又可以作为医疗站使用的医疗运输机，能同时进行士兵部署和伤检治疗，从而减少了伤员重返战场所需的时间。 /// Functioning as both a dropship and a medical bay, medivacs allow for simultaneous troop deployment and triage, reducing the time required to redeploy wounded soldiers.=16505
Skin/Info/MedivacCovertOps,鉴于近些年在隐秘行动任务中战损严重，帝国领导层决定让医疗运输机参与到更多的任务中，期许减少部队伤亡。 /// In response to considerable losses on a recent covert ops mission, the Dominion leadership has approved the use of medivacs on a greater number of assignments, with the goal of reducing casualties.=16506
Skin/Info/MedivacJunker,虽然雇佣兵们习惯了在战场上碰运气，但是有时候在执行涉及到重要人员的任务时，他们还是会使用这一类的改装运输机。 /// Though mercenaries are used to taking their chances in battle, occasionally their missions involve important enough personnel to merit the use of one of these customized medivacs.=16507
Skin/Info/MedivacSilver,尽管机组成员全都是经验丰富的飞行员，泰拉多尔九号星上的医疗运输机干的却主要是营救那些因豪华游艇撞毁在翡翠海暗礁上而被困的有钱人游客。 /// Though staffed by experienced pilots, medivacs on Tyrador IX are mostly used to rescue wealthy tourists who wreck their luxury yachts on reefs in the emerald seas.=16508
Skin/Info/MedivacUmojan,由于受到经年累月的医疗训练，医疗运输机驾驶员的平均寿命一般都比尤摩扬护国军的普通士兵要长。 /// The extensive medical training of medivac pilots has been credited for the longer than average soldier lifespan in the Umojan Protectorate.=16509
Skin/Info/MissileTurret,尽管这些防御建筑很容易被火力清除，但是它们能有效应付空中威胁，同时还能侦测隐匿的敌人。 /// Although these defensive structures are prone to breaking down, they effectively target aerial attackers and are capable of detecting hidden foes.=16510
Skin/Info/MissileTurretCovertOps,得益于其光滑、低调的设计，特战队的导弹炮塔通常不会被发现，直到敌舰直接撞进它们的火力范围。 /// Thanks to their sleek, low-profile design, special forces missile turrets often remain undetected until enemy ships are directly within their line of fire.=16511
Skin/Info/MissileTurretSilver,虽然伊罕利声称他们快速增长的虚空辉光舰队仅用于仪式目的，但为了以防万一，泰拉多尔骑士团已经开始大规模扩大他们的导弹塔网络。=16512
Skin/Info/Mothership,母舰是星灵的终极战舰。常作为星际指挥中心的它，可以独自决定战争结果。它们也是黄金舰队的旗舰。 /// The ultimate protoss vessel, Motherships serve as star-faring command centers that can single-handedly decide the outcome of a battle. They are the flagships of the Golden Armada.=16513
Skin/Info/MothershipGolden,尽管母舰一直都得到了妥善的维护，但是圣堂武士复兴黄金时代的运动，为这些无价的战舰又引来了新一轮的关注与呵护。 /// Though motherships have always been well-maintained, the revival of interest in the golden age of the Templar has resulted in a new wave of support and care for the priceless vessels.=16514
Skin/Info/MothershipIhanrii,伊罕利星灵认为他们自己才是萨尔那加真正唯一的传人，他们自豪地用装饰他们母舰的符文图案来彰显这一信息。 /// The Ihan-rii protoss believe themselves to be the only true descendants of the xel'naga, a message they convey proudly in the runes that adorn their motherships. =16515
Skin/Info/MothershipPurifier,为了不在地位上输给圣堂武士，净化者们开始建造自己的巨型母舰。 /// In the interest of presenting themselves as equals to the templar, the Purifiers have begun constructing their own massive motherships.=16516
Skin/Info/MothershipTaldarim,死亡舰队母舰的作用就是彻底夺取战场控制权。它们每一艘都仿佛是一尊王座，任由塔达林舰队指挥官端坐其上，冷眼漠视着敌人的溃败。 /// The death fleet's motherships are equipped for total battlefield domination. Each one is a throne from which a Tal'darim fleet lord oversees the ruin of their foes.=16517
Skin/Info/Mutalisk,没有什么景象能比看到天空被异龙的双翼布满更令人可怕了。它们排泄出的刃虫共生体可以从高空轻易碾碎整支军队。 /// Few things are as terrifying as a sky blotted out by the wings of mutalisks. The glave wurm symbiotes they expel can easily ravage entire armies from above.=16518
Skin/Info/MutaliskMecha,尽管机械异龙在最初的重量测试中一直进展不顺，不过它最终还是为仿生工程引来了许多新的投资人——其中一些甚至怀有不可告人的目的。 /// Though the mutalisk struggled with initial weight tests, its eventual success led to many new investors for the Simulant Project--some of them with ulterior motivations.=16519
Skin/Info/MutaliskPrimal,原始异龙一直在不停地进化，尤其是它们的双翼和尾部进化得最为频繁。这个变种还减弱了色彩效果，从而让它们在不同环境下可以更好地隐蔽自己。 /// The primal mutalisks are everchanging, particularly when it comes to their wings and tails. This strain also features subdued coloring, allowing them to conceal themselves in many different environments.=16520
Skin/Info/MutaliskRCZ,成群结队的塞伯鲁斯异龙击溃了泰拉多尔九号星上经验不足的维京飞行员们，但当伊罕利星灵乘坐古老的陨石战舰降临时，它们才知道自己遇上了一个更加可怕的对手。 /// Swarms of Cerberus mutalisks outmaneuvered the inexperienced viking pilots defending Tyrador IX, but they faced a tougher foe when the Ihan-rii protoss descended in ancient stone ships.=16521
Skin/Info/MutaliskWebby,异龙是利维坦虫巢所有部队中的绝对主力。据说它们在战斗中按照同一个心智行动，仿佛一团牢不可破的物质遮天蔽日。 /// Mutalisks comprise a vast number of the Leviathan Brood's forces. It is said that they function as one mind in battle, a singular unyielding mass that blacks out the sky.=16522
Skin/Info/Nexus,星灵枢纽相当于一个锚点，让星灵可以连接到跨星系的灵能矩阵当中。最近的技术进步使得这些聚焦点能够操控时间与空间自身。 /// The nexus acts as an anchor allowing protoss to access the psionic matrix across the galaxy. Recent technological advancements have enabled these focal points to manipulate space and time itself.=16523
Skin/Info/NexusForged,很久以前，塔达林对一座被俘获的卡莱星灵枢纽进行了改造，他们使用灵能叉将一颗超载的凯达琳水晶一直约束在其峰值状态，完美体现了他们在建筑残忍美学上的特点。 /// Long ago, the Tal'darim adapted a captured Khalai nexus to maximize its architectural brutality, with a supercharged khaydarin crystal restrained by psionic prongs at its peak. =16524
Skin/Info/NexusIhanrii,伊罕利欢迎人类代表团参观他们的定居点，但人类从来都没有进入过壮观的石制星灵枢纽，那里常常传来诡异的哭泣声和微弱的心跳声。 /// The Ihan-rii welcome terran delegations into their settlements, but never inside their imposing stone nexuses, from which strange ululations and distant heartbeat-sounds emanate.=16525
Skin/Info/NexusRemastered,在母巢之战后，达拉姆派遣了大量相位技师，让他们用最新的时空扭曲技术改造老式的星灵枢纽。 /// Following the Brood War, the Daelaam dedicated a great many phase-smiths to retrofit older nexuses with the latest chronal distortion technology.=16526
Skin/Info/NydusNetwork,虫母想要发动奇袭进而蜂拥性淹没敌人的渴望与坑道虫结合后，催生出了虫道网络。当受到化学刺激时，虫道网络会在地下编织一张巨大的隧道网络，遍及整个战场。 /// Nydus networks evolved from a combination of nydus canals and the desire of broodmothers to surprise and swarm. When activated by chemical stimuli, nydus networks form tunnels underground across the battlefield.=16527
Skin/Info/NydusNetworkMecha,在仿生工程解散后进行的析象扫描显示，未经授权的坑道虫隧道呈蜂窝状遍布于整个设施地下。 /// A scanner sweep conducted after the dissolution of the Simulant Project revealed a convoluted network of unauthorized nydus tunnels honeycombing the facility.=16528
Skin/Info/NydusNetworkRCZ,可远程控制的虫道网络确保了世界各地能同时对泰拉多尔九号星发起第二次入侵，希望这可以促成一个让塞伯鲁斯执行委员会能够接受的结果。 /// Remote-operated nydus networks ensure that the second invasion of Tyrador IX will come from everywhere at once, hopefully facilitating an outcome more palatable to the Cerberus executive board.=16529
Skin/Info/NydusWormMecha,尽管仿生机械坑道虫缺乏本体肌肉骨骼所具备的坚不可摧性，但它的内部气味要好得多。 /// Though the Simulant Project nydus worm lacks the original's musculoskeletal indestructibility, it smells a whole lot better inside.=16530
Skin/Info/Observer,复杂的感应器矩阵让侦测器可以在短时间内采集海量数据。它们提供的关键情报常常扭转战局。 /// Complex sensor matrices allow observers to collect massive amounts of data in a short amount of time. The critical intelligence they provide has turned the tide of battle time and again.=16531
Skin/Info/ObserverGolden,老式侦测器使用的是一套不同的稳定器配置，尽管新式的在功能上没什么不同，但它们看起来更唬人。一些相位技师声称它的性能也大幅提高了，但这一点并未得到验证。 /// Older observers had a different stabilizer configuration that, though equally effective, gave them with a more imposing aspect. Some phase-smiths claim that it also boosts performance, but this is unverified. =16532
Skin/Info/ObserverIhanrii,几千年来，伊罕利星灵部署了大量的侦测器来监视其他星灵部族和异虫，完全不担心会被发现。 /// For millennia, the Ihan-rii have deployed observers to monitor the other protoss sects and the zerg without concern of being discovered.=16533
Skin/Info/ObserverPurifier,侦测器在净化者部队中是非常珍贵的，尤其深受菲尼克斯本人的喜爱。 /// Observers are greatly prized among the Purifier forces, having found especially strong favor with Fenix himself.=16534
Skin/Info/ObserverTaldarim,侦察是执行战术欺骗和战术抉择的基本条件。最狡诈的晋升者们广泛地使用侦测器来侦察斯雷恩的敌人……亦或是彼此。 /// Reconnaissance is essential for effective deception and subterfuge. The most cunning ascendants make extensive use of observers to spy on Slayn's enemies... and on each other.=16535
Skin/Info/Oracle,在被艾尔长年流放期间，奈拉齐姆可以无拘无束地使用新技术进行各种实验。灵活敏捷的先知船就是他们探索研究取得的成果之一。 /// During their long exile from Aiur, the Nerazim were free to experiment with new technologies. The agile oracle vessels are an excellent example of how fruitful this exploration could be.=16536
Skin/Info/OracleGolden,圣堂武士传统主义者也一样会借鉴奈拉齐姆科技，只是他们会做一些美学上的改进，以符合他们所喜好的样式。对于这种做法，女族长沃拉尊拒绝发表评论。 /// Templar traditionalists still borrow technology from the Nerazim, choosing to change only the aesthetics to suit their preferences. Matriarch Vorazun has declined to comment on this practice.=16537
Skin/Info/OracleIhanrii,伊罕利派出了先知船去调查在泰拉多尔九号星轨道上向他们靠近的一艘贝希摩斯级战列巡航舰。 /// The Ihan-rii dispatched oracles to investigate the Behemoth-class battlecruiser that approached them in orbit around Tyrador IX.=16538
Skin/Info/OraclePurifier,尽管一开始在设计上困难重重，智慧高超的相位技师们还是成功地造出了与奈拉齐姆先知类似的舰船。 /// Though initially beset by design challenges, clever phase-smiths have been able to engineer vessels similar to the Nerazim oracles.=16539
Skin/Info/OracleTaldarim,塔达林对奈拉齐姆的时空控制技术垂涎已久。成功盗取的先知船被控制它们的舰队领主们满腹狐疑地看守着。 /// The Tal'darim have long coveted the Nerazim's temporal mastery. Stolen oracles are jealously guarded by the fleet lords who control them.=16540
Skin/Info/OrbitalCommandCovertOps,轨道控制基地的尖端扫描仪省去了大多数的侦察任务——这大大减轻了通常负责定位敌人的一线陆战队员们的负担。 /// The cutting-edge scanners on this orbital command render most reconnaissance missions unnecessary – much to the relief of the low-ranking marines usually tasked with locating the enemy.=16541
Skin/Info/OverSeerWebby,为强化侦察能力而培育出来的利维坦眼虫，其鳍条和触须能让它们在空气和水中毫不费力地穿行。 /// Bred to specialize in reconnaissance, the fins and tendrils of the Leviathan overseers allow them to cut through both air and water with minimal effort.=16542
Skin/Info/Overlord,王虫在异虫巢群中扮演着极为关键的角色，它们负责喷洒菌毯以及中继传输虫母发送给次级异虫指令的任务。 /// Overlords perform a critical function for a zerg hive cluster-- spreading creep and relaying psionic commands from a broodmother to the less evolved organisms she controls. =16543
Skin/Info/OverlordMecha,作为仿生工程的一项早期作品，机械王虫受到了一名实验室科学家的严格控制，以保证它能在整个运行期间一直处于一个安全的临界点范围内。 /// An early creation during the course of the Simulant Project, the overlord is carefully controlled by a lab scientist, making it a critical safety point in the entire operation.=16544
Skin/Info/OverlordPrimal,一些原始异虫族群领袖，比如德哈卡，虽然进化出了远超王虫需求的能力，但是大都丧失了过去的痕迹。 /// Some primal zerg pack leaders, like Dehaka, have evolved beyond the need of overlords, but a few of them nonetheless remain as vestiges of the past.=16545
Skin/Info/OverlordRCZ,塞伯鲁斯王虫可以使用炽热的能量信标来精确定位，即便是在低能见度的环境中，比如泰拉多尔九号星上常见的沙尘暴和浓雾层。 /// Cerberus overlords use incandescent energy beacons to pinpoint positioning even in low-visibility conditions, like the dust storms and fog banks common on Tyrador IX.=16546
Skin/Info/OverlordWebby,王虫负责对异虫爪牙施加控制力。由于受到它们彼此之间长期联络的影响，利维坦虫巢的王虫们自身也出现了地表异虫的基因特征。 /// Overlords exert control over the minions of the zerg. As a result of their constant connection, the Leviathan Brood's overlords reflect the genetic mutations of the creatures beneath them.=16547
Skin/Info/OverlordXPR,由于王虫需要同时为多种不同的异虫变种提供支持，所以她们有时能表现出一些本能的适应性突变，以提高她们自身的效能。 /// Due to their need to support many different strains of zerg at once, overlords can sometimes exhibit spontaneous adaptive mutations in an attempt to improve their own efficiency.=16548
Skin/Info/Overseer,由王虫进化而来的眼虫专注于侦察和揭示隐形敌人的踪迹，无论敌人潜伏在哪里。 /// Evolved from the overlord, the overseer focuses its eyes towards scouting and revealing the presence of hidden enemies, wherever they may lurk.=16549
Skin/Info/OverseerMecha,由于无法完全复制眼虫的眼球生物结构，首席工程师不得不退而求其次，选择使用探测扫描器来实现大部分功能，只是这样做不太美观。 /// Unable to fully replicate the organic structure behind the overseer's eyes, the head engineer replaced them with detection sensors that fulfill largely the same purpose—aside from the aesthetics. =16550
Skin/Info/OverseerPrimal,作为原始异虫中最稀有的物种之一，眼虫几乎难得一见。和它们在虫群里的同行类似，它们是由原始王虫变异而来，拥有极其敏锐的感知力。 /// One of the rarest species of primal zerg, the overseers are seldom seen. Like their Swarm counterparts, they evolved from primal overlords and possess especially keen senses.=16551
Skin/Info/OverseerRCZ,塞伯鲁斯眼虫的虚空感应器科技是由鲁道夫·萨布索里安博士研发的。它可以三角测量出20公里内任何隐形效果的确切位置。 /// The Cerberus overseer's void sensor technology was developed by one Dr. Rudolfo Subsourian. It can triangulate the exact position of a cloaking effect within 20 kilometers.=16552
Skin/Info/Phoenix,为执行空中侵扰任务而设计的凤凰战机，因其拥有无可匹敌的速度和机动性而闻名。即便是在寡不敌众的局面下，单支打击部队也能把敌军耗在原地。 /// Designed for aerial harassment, phoenixes are known for their unmatched speed and maneuverability. A single strike force can keep an enemy army pinned down even when vastly outnumbered.=16553
Skin/Info/PhoenixGolden,席拉克部族使用的凤凰战机与早期仲裁官们青睐的护卫船非常相似。虽然有些人对它们的象征性抱有争议，但也有些人对它们精美的工艺赞不绝口。 /// The Shelak tribe has commissioned phoenixes that resemble the escort ships favored by early judicators. Though some see them as controversial symbols, others praise the beautiful craftsmanship.=16554
Skin/Info/PhoenixIhanrii,尽管伊罕利凤凰战机的陨石构造并没有限制它的机动性或最高速度，但是这种材质却使凤凰战机在紧急迫降时成了一种拥有更高动能的高空坠落物。 /// Though the Ihan-rii phoenix's stone construction doesn't inhibit its maneuverability or top speed, it does make it a more formidable missile when crash-landing.=16555
Skin/Info/PhoenixPurifier,当净化者们不需要幻影战机的相位技术时，它们就会部署机械凤凰战机来防御自己的领空。 /// When the Purifiers do not need the phasing technology of the mirages, they will deploy robotic phoenixes to defend their skies.=16556
Skin/Info/PhoenixTaldarim,战场上有时候需要以雷霆万钧之势碾压敌人，有时候又得以鬼魅袭扰之法偷袭敌人。塔达林明白后一种战法的价值。正因为如此，他们维持着一支从圣堂武士那里盗来的凤凰战机舰队。 /// There is a time for overwhelming force, and a time to be swift and deadly. The Tal'darim recognize the value in the latter, which is why they maintain a fleet of phoenixes stolen from the Templar.=16557
Skin/Info/PhotonCannon,星灵的相位技师们可以为他们的防御性建筑配备强大的反物质火炮和先进的侦测设备，但是将光子炮和折跃科技结合起来的实验普遍以失败告终。 /// Protoss phase-smiths can outfit their defensive structures with powerful antimatter cannons and advanced detection measures. Experiments integrating photon cannons with warp technology widely ended in failure.=16558
Skin/Info/PhotonCannonForged,尽管他们一直恪守严格的战士准则，但是塔达林对秘密建造光子炮来摧毁敌人的采矿线这种事情完全没有意见。 /// Despite their commitment to a rigid warrior code, the Tal'darim have no problem building photon cannons in secret to rain devastation on their enemies' mineral lines. =16559
Skin/Info/PhotonCannonIhanrii,伊罕利光子炮台上面的相位碎裂炮具有独特机翼形状的外壳，它的设计灵感来源于一种雄伟的鸟类生物。这种生物曾统治着泰拉多尔九号星的天空，至少在它们被早期的人类定居者捕杀灭绝之前是这样。 /// The phase disruptor housing of the Ihan-rii photon cannon features a distinctive wing-shape inspired by a majestic avian creature that once ruled Tyrador IX's skies, at least until it was hunted to extinction by early terran settlers.=16560

Skin/Info/Probe,被卡莱设计用来搭建星灵定居点的探机，是一种自给自足的无人机。它们可以启动和执行关键性预制建筑的折跃任务。 /// Designed by the Khalai to lay the foundation for protoss settlements, probes are self-sufficient drones that can enable and initiate the warp-in of critical prefabricated structures.=16563
Skin/Info/ProbeBlizzcon17,这些探机是一群飞车党从消亡的星灵殖民地里回收的，他们还使用人类的引擎和配件对其进行了改装。这种工艺的确与众不同。 /// These probes were salvaged from a destroyed protoss colony by members of a junker gang, who then retrofitted them with terran engines and accessories. If nothing else, their craftsmanship is unique.=16564
Skin/Info/ProbeGolden,自从万世之战结束后的那个时代起，就有少量的探机一直幸存至今。在那个时代，即便是最简单的星灵机械造物也有着精美与奢华的外观。 /// A small number of probes have survived since the period following the Aeon of Strife, where even the simplest of protoss robotics had a refined and luxurious appearance.=16565
Skin/Info/ProbeIhanrii,当处于长时间深空休眠不需要工作时，伊罕利探机会折叠成完美的立方体，以便能紧凑存放。 /// When not in use during long periods of deep-space hibernation, Ihan-rii probes fold into perfect cubes for compact storage.=16566
Skin/Info/ProbePurifier,这些探机是效率与勤劳的楷模。它们运行的是一套加强版的程序协议，完全集成了净化者的数据网。 /// These probes are models of efficiency and diligence. They operate on enhanced protocols for full integration with the Purifier data web.=16567
Skin/Info/ProbeRemastered,全面战争纪元前的探机拥有更长的稳定鳍，但是相位技师们很快就发现，这种设计在大规模激烈的战斗中反而是个妨碍。=16568
Skin/Info/ProbeTaldarim,达拉姆使用的探机都会被进行校正，使其在采集资源的同时尽可能减少对生态的影响。塔达林则对这种预防措施完全无感。 /// Probes utilized by the Daelaam are calibrated to gather resources with as little ecological impact as possible. The Tal'darim have no use for such precautions.=16569
Skin/Info/Pylon,铸造一个全新的灵能矩阵一直是达拉姆重建工作中的重中之重。每一座水晶塔内的凯达琳水晶，都能使星灵接入矩阵能量中。 /// Forging a new psionic matrix has been vital to the Daelaam's reconstruction efforts. The khaydarin crystal within each pylon allows the protoss to tap into the matrix's energy.=16570
Skin/Info/PylonForged,每一座塔达林水晶塔都不断发出噼啪的灵能爆裂声，充盈的能量足以驱动十六座传送门。 /// Each Tal'darim pylon crackles with enough psionic energy to power sixteen gateways.=16571
Skin/Info/PylonIhanrii,伊罕利在泰拉多尔九号星上重新殖民。在殖民区域中，那些发着冷光的水晶塔阵不断扩大，散发着飘忽的光芒，即使是在轨道中也能看到。=16572

Skin/Info/Queen,为了守护虫群的未来，凯瑞甘精心设计了一种全新的虫后物种。它们能够独立思考和分析，充当着不断进化的虫群的虫巢主人。 /// To safeguard the future of the Swarm, Kerrigan orchestrated the creation a new breed of queens. Capable of independent thought and analysis, they serve as the hive masters of an ever-evolving Swarm.=16575
Skin/Info/QueenMecha,华丽的虫后是第一个完成生产后就失踪的型号。由于不想让公众得知它们的存在，仿生工程的经理们不得不秘密调查此事。 /// The magnificent queen was the first completed production model to go missing. Loath to publicly reveal their activities, the Simulant Project managers investigated the matter as quietly as possible.=16576
Skin/Info/QueenPrimal,原始异虫族群崇尚力量至上。正因为如此，与传统虫巢里的虫后比起来，原始虫后在族群中的地位非比寻常，少数留下来的都是强者中的强者。 /// Primal packs are ruled by strength alone, therefore queens occupy a much different position within them versus more traditional broods, and are rarely present in great numbers.=16577
Skin/Info/QueenRCZ,塞伯鲁斯虫后配备了锻造钛金刀片和喷气动力尖刺发射器，它们出于母亲般的本能守护着虫群的后防线，即便是神经系统重做也无法完全消除这种本能。 /// Queens defend the Cerberus backline with forged titanium blades, jet-powered spine launchers, and matronly instincts even a neurological overhaul couldn't eliminate entirely. =16578
Skin/Info/QueenWebby,即便是利维坦虫巢的虫后都是极其凶恶和富有攻击性。任何心怀敌意想要接近它们的愚蠢生物，很快就会发现自己变成一副扎满脊刺的尸体。 /// Even the queens of the Leviathan Brood are incredibly vicious and hostile. Any creatures foolish enough to approach their clutch with hostile intent find themselves quickly impaled by many spines.=16579
Skin/Info/Ravager,从经历了多年基因改造的蟑螂身上进化而来的破坏者，拥有一项极其特殊的能力。它们可以在短时间内快速产生大量腐蚀胆汁，然后朝敌人喷泄。 /// Evolved from roaches after years of genetic modification, ravagers possess the ability to quickly generate massive quantities of corrosive bile and then expel them at their foes.=16580
Skin/Info/RavagerBone,异虫甲壳钙化成一层坚硬的外壳，可作为极其有效的护甲。阿巴瑟觉得这一吓阻因素聊胜于无。 /// Calcification of zerg carapaces into a hardened shell makes for effective armor. Abathur considers the intimidation factor a welcome bonus.=16581
Skin/Info/RavagerMecha,仿生机械破坏者在它们的等离子火焰容器周围装备了吸热板，而非吸热钉，以防止其它部位遭到损坏。 /// Simulant ravagers have been fitted with heat-absorbent panels instead of spikes around their plasma fire receptacles to prevent damage to the rest of the model. =16582
Skin/Info/RavagerPrimal,挑衅叛逆且残忍嗜血，原始破坏者甚至连自己的幼子都会吞食，如果后者没有足够的力量反抗的话。也正因为它们拥有极强的侵略性，这个品种能延续多久还是个未知数。 /// Defiant and bloodthirsty, the primal ravagers will devour their own young if they are not strong enough to fight back. Given this level of aggression, it is uncertain how long their species will thrive.=16583
Skin/Info/RavagerRCZ,塞伯鲁斯破坏者背部的等离子尖刺会急速加热背部喷出的腐蚀胆汁。这些破坏者在泰拉多尔九号星上把泰伦人的防御砸得千疮百孔。 /// The plasma spines on the Cerberus ravager's back superheat the corrosive bile it fires. On Tyrador IX, these ravagers punched massive holes in the terran defense.=16584
Skin/Info/RavagerWebby,体型巨大、面目可憎，完全进化后的破坏者是一种令人不敢目视的恐怖存在。而利维坦虫巢培育出的这种梦魇般怪物只会更加可怕。 /// Monstrous and towering, the fully evolved ravager is a terrifying sight to behold. The webbed nightmares deployed by the Leviathan Brood are only more so.=16585
Skin/Info/Raven,铁鸦在监控和防御方面具有不可估量的作用，它们能部署炮塔，建造防御无人机，或者朝敌方部队发射飞弹。不仅如此，在费效比方面，它也比前任更高。 /// Invaluable for surveillance and defense, the raven can construct a turret, build a defense drone, or fire missiles at enemy forces. If this wasn't enough, it's also more cost effective than its predecessors.=16586
Skin/Info/RavenCovertOps,帝国特战队的骄傲，这种精密设计的飞行器据说能侦测到地下两公里深处的凯莫瑞安矿工之间的对话。 /// The pride of the Dominion Special Forces, this exquisitely designed craft is rumored to be able to detect Kel-Morian miners whispering to each other two kilometers underground.=16587
Skin/Info/RavenJunker,极其先进的侦察装备虽然不是雇佣兵的最爱，但是在锈迹斑斑的涂装之下，这些铁鸦的作战性能丝毫不逊于帝国正规军。 /// Highly advanced surveillance craft aren't the most popular among mercenaries, but beneath the rust and cracking paint, these ravens are as good as any others in the Dominion.=16588
Skin/Info/RavenSilver,正当塞伯鲁斯异虫威胁要击溃泰拉多尔九号星的守护军时，一只高空飞行的铁鸦突然在这颗行星的重力井中侦测到了一支奇怪的陨石舰队。 /// As the Cerberus zerg threatened to overwhelm Tyrador IX's defenders, a high-altitude raven detected a fleet of strange stone ships in the planet's gravity well.=16589

Skin/Info/Reactor,在研究星灵的约束力场时，泰伦科学家取得了一项重大突破，使得指挥官们可以将他们的生产能力提高一倍。 /// While researching protoss containment fields, terran scientists made a breakthrough that allowed commanders to double their production capacity.=16591

Skin/Info/Reaper,那些很难接受再社会化教育的新兵都会被训练成收割者。由于具有高度的侵略性并且时常怀有侥幸心理，这些突击队员们很少有人活着退役。 /// Recruits who prove resistant to resocialization are trained as Reapers. Hyper-aggressive and prone to taking risks, these shock troopers seldom survive a full tour of duty.=16594

Skin/Info/ReaperUmojan,经过多年的建档挑选后，尤摩扬护国军终于从心理学上筛选出足够多的候选者，来创建他们自己的收割者部队，整支部队的战斗力好得令人意外。 /// Over the course of many years, the Umojan Protectorate was able to psychologically profile enough suitable candidates to create their own Reaper Corps with surprisingly good results.=16598
Skin/Info/Refinery,精炼厂的设计初衷就是为了萃取原生高能瓦斯，然后用便携式的圆桶进行储藏，以方便太空工程车进行运输。 /// The refinery is designed to extract raw vespene gas and package it into a handy cylinder, which is easily transportable by space construction vehicles.=16599
Skin/Info/RefineryCovertOps,特战队精炼厂采集高能瓦斯的速度和常规型号一样快，但是产生的噪音减少了75%。 /// The special forces refinery harvests vespene just as fast as the regulation model, but produces 75% less noise.=16600
Skin/Info/RefinerySilver,尽管进行了勤奋的维护，但自从塞伯鲁斯袭击以来，泰拉多尔九号星的精炼厂报告称他们的高能瓦斯产量低于平均水平，就好像他们开采的地下气泉被分流了一样。=16601
Skin/Info/Roach,蟑螂是被刀锋女王亲自选中同化并加入虫群的。其令人惊叹的组织重生能力以及强酸毒液，使得它们不仅极其致命而且生存力强。 /// Roaches were hand-selected by the Queen of Blades for assimilation into the Swarm. Their impressive tissue regeneration and acidic venom make them resilient as well as deadly.=16602
Skin/Info/RoachDeluxe,听命于扎加拉的阿巴瑟为了寻求最完美的基因结构，一直在操控异虫基因。蟑螂独有的恢复能力使其成为了最理想的研究对象。 /// Under Zagara's orders, Abathur has continued to manipulate the zerg genome in search of perfection. The roach's innate regenerative abilities make it the ideal candidate for such a pursuit.=16603
Skin/Info/RoachMecha,这些机械装备了一套复杂的自我修复系统，以模拟蟑螂那不可思议的治愈能力，同时还能抵消其强酸储液所造成的结构性损坏。 /// These machines have been outfitted with a sophisticated self-repair system to replicate the roach's incredible healing ability, while also combatting structural damage from its acid reserves.=16604
Skin/Info/RoachPrimal,蟑螂是第一批被泽鲁斯星球上的原始族群所吸纳的虫种，它们进化出了能变异成原始点火虫和原始守护者的能力。 /// Roaches were among the first to be absorbed into primal packs on Zerus, where they developed the capability to mutate into primal igniters and primal guardians.=16605
Skin/Info/RoachRCZ,塞伯鲁斯科学家们用碳纤维纳米编织技术加固了蟑螂原本就已经十分坚固的盔甲。此外还给它添加了锻造的钛金刀片，进一步提升其进攻能力。 /// Cerberus scientists bulwarked the roach's already-impressive armor with a carbon fiber nanoweave. Forged titanium blades were added to aid its offensive capabilities as well.=16606
Skin/Info/RoachWarren,产生蟑螂和破坏者需要潮湿黑暗的环境。蟑螂温室是一种构造完美的生物器官，可以准确地复制出这种环境。 /// Generating roaches and ravagers requires humid, dark conditions. The roach warren is a perfectly constructed biological organ that replicates this environment precisely.=16607
Skin/Info/RoachWarrenMecha,研发仿生机械蟑螂温室的前提是必须要在聚合物合金材料上取得重大突破，只有这样蟑螂温室的外壳才能经受住其内部强酸生成时所诱发的不稳反应。 /// Significant polymer-alloy innovations were necessary to develop a housing for the Simulant roach warren that would withstand the turmoil of its internal acid generation.=16608
