Skin/Info/SupplyDepotXPR,经历了痛失继承人的悲剧之后，“天使航运”决定重操旧业。这家公司保证以优惠的价格，提前将货物送达前线。 /// After the tragic loss of its heir apparent, Angel Shipping is back in business. The company's shipments are guaranteed to arrive on the frontline ahead of schedule and under budget.=16671
Skin/Info/SwarmHost,虫群极其擅长增生繁殖，尤其是丑陋的虫群宿主。通过快速生产大量的蝗虫，单单一只虫群宿主就可以淹没一支敌军。 /// The Swarm excels at proliferation, especially the hideous Swarm Host. By rapidly birthing multitudes of locusts, a single Swarm Host can overwhelm an enemy army.=16672
Skin/Info/SwarmHostMecha,在攻关虫群宿主的功能结构设计期间，工程师们相继病倒。然而，安全系统并未上报这一情况，生产工作也照常进行，死亡事件也无人处理。 /// Engineers began to fall ill while working on the swarm host mechanics. However, the safety systems did not report a problem, and production continued undisturbed—fatalities aside.=16673
Skin/Info/SwarmHostPrimal,这些生物演变成了原始宿主的一个分支，它们曾是所有虫群宿主的起源。如今，在命运神奇的交汇下，这些变种再次合为一体。 /// These creatures have developed as an offshoot of the primal hosts, who were the progenitors of all swarm hosts. Now, through a surprising twist of fate, the strains have merged once more.=16674
Skin/Info/SwarmHostRCZ,塞伯鲁斯虫群宿主的体内有一个微型工厂，可以为每一只蝗虫装配远程控制头部装置。 /// The Cerberus swarm host contains an internal microfactory that equips each locust with remote-control headgear.=16675
Skin/Info/SwarmHostWebby,利维坦虫巢的虫群宿主尤其擅长两栖攻击。它们携带的许多基因优点能让它们快速跨越海洋，追捕猎物。 /// The swarm hosts of the Leviathan Brood are uniquely specialized for amphibious assault and bear many genetic advantages that allow them to move quickly through the oceans and assail their prey.=16676
Skin/Info/TechLab,一旦作战建筑建成，承担研发工作的小型科技实验室就会在它们旁边建立起来。这类工作中有一部分具有很大的危险性，但是这都被认为是支援战争所要承受的必不可少的牺牲。 /// Once combat buildings are established, small tech labs are built alongside them to undertake research and development work. Some of this work can be dangerous, but it is seen essential to the war effort.=16677
Skin/Info/TechLabCovertOps,特战队的科技实验室使用从帝国星灵盟友那里偷来的纳米科技，最大限度地提高能源效率和研发速度。 /// The special forces tech lab uses nanotechnology pilfered from the Dominion's protoss allies to maximize energy efficiency and research speed.=16678
Skin/Info/TechLabSilver,泰拉多尔骑士团的科技实验室配有最顶尖的气候控制系统，可以在该星球的温度总是剧烈变化的情况下时刻保持最高效率。=16679
Skin/Info/Tempest,风暴战舰虽然是黄金舰队的新晋战舰，但是在舰队最强大战船的名单里成功占据了一席之地。它们可怕的衰变武器是一支不可被忽视的力量。 /// Tempests are a recent addition to the Golden Armada, and have earned their place as one of the fleet’s most powerful warships. Their volatile disintegration weaponry is a force to be reckoned with.=16680
Skin/Info/TempestGolden,经过一系列实验后，相位技师们开始使用高亮光泽的装饰性板甲制造自定义的风暴战舰，这种板甲可以经受住战舰产生的动能矩阵的毁灭性能量。 /// After some experimentation, phase-smiths created customized tempests with high-sheen ornamental plating that could withstand the destructive energies of the vessel's kinetic matrix.=16681
Skin/Info/TempestIhanrii,伊罕利风暴战舰的陨石材质表面具有阻尼效果，这一特性增强了它的一项能力，使其可以将动能矩阵不可思议的能量输出进一步聚焦。 /// The dampening effect of the Ihan-rii tempest's stone surface enhances its ability to focus the incredible power output of its kinetic matrix.=16682
Skin/Info/TempestPurifier,这种遥控驾驶的战舰是净化者军团取得的几大主要成就之一。与同类型战舰相比最明显的区别就是，它的机体上使用了塞布罗斯造板甲。 /// This remotely piloted vessel is one of the signature achievements of the Purifier program, and its Cybros manufactured plating is among the most distinctive of its kind.=16683
Skin/Info/TempestTaldarim,达拉姆时不时就会让塔达林震惊一下。风暴战舰的诞生就是其中一个例子。首次在战斗中亮相就让高阶领主下定决心要将其纳入死亡舰队的麾下。 /// Occasionally, the Daelaam impress the Tal'darim. The creation of the tempest was one such moment. Upon first seeing them in combat, the Highlord vowed to seize them for the death fleet.=16684
Skin/Info/TemplarArchive,高阶圣堂武士在圣堂武士文献馆中访问和学习前辈们的记忆和经历，以此磨练和提高自己的灵能技艺。 /// The high templar hone their psionic abilities at the templar archives by accessing and studying the memories and experiences of their predecessors.=16685
Skin/Info/TemplarArchiveForged,在战斗间隙，升格之链排名靠前的塔达林战士可以访问圣堂武士文献馆，重温他们最英勇的事迹。 /// In between battles, Tal'darim warriors ranked highly on the Chain of Ascension can visit the templar archives to relive their most heroic feats.=16686
Skin/Info/TemplarArchiveIhanrii,伊罕利的圣堂武士文献馆中保存着该文明最严密保守的秘密，其中包括宗教文献和那些令人毛骨悚然的半有机可变形陨石的使用说明。=16687
Skin/Info/Thor,雷神可谓泰伦人军事力量的终极诠释，其所配备的强大火力足以消灭一整支敌方部队。 /// The ultimate expression of terran military might, the Thor is outfitted with enough artillery to take down an army of enemy combatants on its own.=16688
Skin/Info/ThorCE,强化雷神的作战性能已成为帝国工程师之间相互较劲的一项不成文的现象。高层也对此默不作声，只要能制造出更强大的攻城步战机甲就行。 /// Improving on the Thor has become an informal competition amongst Dominion engineers. Top brass is content with allowing this trend to continue, as long as it results in more powerful siege walkers.=16689
Skin/Info/ThorCovertOps,作为近些年兵器研发的标志性成就之一，帝国特战队的雷神自称配备了数不清的升级科技并且运用了最新的精钢板甲改良工艺。 /// A signature achievement in recent weapons engineering, the Dominion Special Forces thor boasts innumerable upgrades and the latest in neosteel plating advancements.=16690
Skin/Info/ThorJunker,米拉的手下们一直渴望能拥有他们自己的雷神，但是复杂的建造工艺一度令他们望而却步。如今，他们终于找到了办法来组装可以正常运转的雷神了…… /// Mira's crew has long desired a Thor of their own, but construction challenges routinely set them back. Any day now, they could find a way to assemble one that is fully functional...=16691
Skin/Info/ThorSilver,泰拉多尔雷神全都经过钚涂层处理，可以使来袭炮弹偏斜到一定的能量阈值以下。这种涂层在阅兵式上也更好看。 /// Tyrador thors are treated with a plutonium coating that deflects projectiles below a certain energy threshold. They also look great in parades.=16692
Skin/Info/ThorUmojan,经过多年不懈的探索后，尤摩扬护国军终于找到了能够对帝国雷神做出回应的答案，其令人震撼的外形与其所涂装的尤摩扬标志数量完美贴合。 /// After years of fervent exploration, the Umojan Protectorate has finally come up with its answer to the Dominion's Thor, and its impressiveness is only matched by the number of Umojan symbols it sports.=16693
Skin/Info/TwilightCouncil,光影议会是达拉姆代表们举行会议的场所，他们在这里讨论各种关乎星灵未来的议题。 /// The twilight council serves as a meeting place for representatives of the Daelaam to discuss the betterment of all protoss.=16694
Skin/Info/TwilightCouncilForged,塔达林的光影议会也是一个偷来的卡莱建筑，只是它们的建筑风格变得更加令人生畏、更加晦暗，不过其所提供的升级科技并无变化。 /// Another stolen Khalai structure, the Tal'darim twilight council's architecture is more intimidating and somber, though the upgrades it bestows are identical.=16695
Skin/Info/TwilightCouncilIhanrii,在回到家乡阿拉基尔之后，伊罕利议会的长老们发现这个地方既熟悉，但又令人不安。在他们离开的漫长岁月里，许多事情都发生了变化，空气质量大不如前，受人喜爱的物种也走向了灭绝，而这都要归因于人类的发展。=16696
Skin/Info/Ultralisk,雷兽因其体型和力量而闻名。它们的重甲壳几乎是无法穿透的，而它们巨大的螯刺可以轻而易举地撕裂敌人。 /// Ultralisks are legendary for their size and strength. Their armored carapaces are nearly impenetrable, and their gargantuan pincers can both crush and eviscerate their enemies with ease.=16697
Skin/Info/UltraliskCE,雷兽就像它的体型一样强大，充满破坏力。尤其是在灌注了泽鲁斯原始异虫的精华之后，它们几乎成为了不可阻挡的杀戮机器。 /// Ultralisks are powerful and destructive enough as they are. When infused with the essence of Zerus's primal zerg, however, they become truly unstoppable killing machines.=16698
Skin/Info/UltraliskCavern,这个洞窟里面充满了危险的放射性生物沉积物。里面产生的化学反应被用来制造雷兽所需要的基因代码。 /// This cavern is filled with dangerous biological deposits infused with high radiation. The chemical reactions created within are used to build the genetic code required for the ultralisk.=16699
Skin/Info/UltraliskCavernMecha,仿生机械雷兽窟将其放射性内部结构安置在一个改装的战列巡航舰引擎隔热罩内。 /// The Simulant Project ultralisk cavern houses its radioactive innards within a converted battlecruiser engine heatshield.=16700
Skin/Info/UltraliskCavernRCZ,这座雷兽窟每个小时能够产出三副闪闪发光的钛金刀片，看起来真可怕，不过如果知道内幕的话就没那么可怕了——就像一位塞伯鲁斯副总裁曾在视察时流露出挖苦的表情一样——毕竟雷兽嘴巴上方发出的光看起来就像萌萌的小眼睛。=16701
Skin/Info/UltraliskMecha,在仿生工程初期，主创团队一致同意绝不会制造一台雷兽复制品。但是后来实验室陷入一片混乱后，这份协议也被抛诸脑后了。 /// Early in the project, it was agreed that the team would never construct a replica of the ultralisk. When chaos later overtook the lab, it became clear that the agreement had been broken...=16702
Skin/Info/UltraliskPrimal,原始雷兽在外表上呈现出高度的多样性。有些很像虫群里的雷兽，还有些则因为适应泽鲁斯环境而进化出了不同的生物特征。 /// Primal ultralisks exhibit a high level of variety in their appearance, with some closely resembling the Swarm ultralisks, and others adapting different features better suited to life on Zerus.=16703
Skin/Info/UltraliskRCZ,塞伯鲁斯销售团队总会尽可能地给潜在的客户们展示可远程操控的雷兽。经过烧蓝处理的那副钛金巨型刀片植体看上去确实令人赏心悦目。 /// Cerberus sales teams always make sure to show prospective clients the remote-control ultralisk. Their heat-treated titanium blade implants are a beautiful sight to behold.=16704
Skin/Info/UltraliskRemastered,与现今的雷兽相比，早期的雷兽在体型上更加苗条，动作上也更灵活，浑身都是坚韧强健的肌肉与筋腱，而非笨重的装甲。 /// Early ultralisks were slimmer and more agile than their modern-day counterparts, with swaths of durable muscle and sinew instead of bulky armor.=16705
Skin/Info/UltraliskWebby,很少有其它活体生物能比得上雷兽的绝对力量。而那些从利维坦虫巢中诞生的怪兽更是一种完全由利刃和脊刺组成的恐怖存在，仿佛只应存在于传说之中。 /// Few other living creatures can match the sheer might of the ultralisks. Those birthed by the Leviathan Brood are terrifying visages of spines and blades--monsters worthy of legend.=16706
Skin/Info/Viking,为了加强泰伦帝国防空部队实力而研发的维京战机，由于有两种多功能战斗模式，进而成为了当代的一个经典兵种。 /// Developed to bolster the Terran Dominion's anti-air forces, the Viking is a modern classic thanks to its two versatile combat modes.=16707
Skin/Info/VikingCovertOps,帝国研究者们在现有的维京战机设计上增添了一组全新双发引擎，使其在两种模式下的火力都得以提升。 /// Dominion researchers have added a new set of twin engines to complement the existing design of the viking, while increasing its firepower in both modes.=16708
Skin/Info/VikingJunker,米拉的机械师们给他们的维京战机加装了大量特殊装备，其中就包括巨型双发引擎。踩到最高转速时，轰鸣声震耳欲聋。 /// Mira's mechanics have given their Vikings a number of special additions, including massive twin engines that produce an impressively intimidating roar when fully revved.=16709
Skin/Info/VikingMecha,在瓦伦里安大帝的命令下，卡斯蒂略工业取得了突破性的维京战机科技。他们的原型机融入了更时髦与更高效的工艺。 /// Under Emperor Valerian's orders, Castillo Industries has developed a breakthrough in Viking technology. Their prototype features a sleeker and more efficient construction.=16710
Skin/Info/VikingSilver,一到了晚上，这架维京战机喷出的蓝色尾焰在几公里外都可以看到，这让游客们感到很安心，知道有泰拉多尔骑士团在守护着他们。 /// At night, the stunning blue thrusters on this viking can be spotted from miles away, reassuring tourists that the Knights of Tyrador are watching over them.=16711
Skin/Info/VikingUmojan,经过一场漫长的谈判后，卡斯蒂略工业同意生产一种配备重型板甲的全新维京机型，专供尤摩扬护国军使用。 /// After a protracted negotiation, Castillo Industries has agreed to manufacture a new, heavily plated Viking model exclusively for the Umojan Protectorate.=16712
Skin/Info/Viper,原本属于原始异虫一部分的飞蛇，其基因序列被阿巴瑟纳入了虫群。如今，它们作为工具按照其主人的意愿操控着战场。 /// Originally a part of the primal zerg, the vipers' sequences were incorporated into the Swarm by Abathur himself. Now, they serve as a tool to manipulate the battlefield to their master's liking.=16713
Skin/Info/ViperMecha,在仿生工程临近尾声之际，董事会们愈发关注他们到底创造了什么，代价又是几何。但是在这点上，工程负责人们一直含糊其辞。 /// As the Simulant Project neared its completion, the directors became increasingly concerned about what they had created—and at what cost. The project owners stopped answering questions around this point.=16714
Skin/Info/ViperPrimal,最初的飞蛇品种拥有大量特有的恶毒防御能力，后来它们被阿巴瑟盯上并作为进一步进化的主要候选品种也就不奇怪了。 /// The original viper specimens possess a number of uniquely vicious defenses, making it no surprise that they came to Abathur's attention as prime candidates for further evolution.=16715
Skin/Info/ViperRCZ,安装了锤状颅骨植体后的飞蛇，其喙的缠绕精准度显著提高了。 /// Vipers with hammerhead cranial implants demonstrate dramatic increases in prehensile proboscis precision.=16716
Skin/Info/ViperWebby,作为最初异虫虫巢中的一员，利维坦飞蛇比起其它虫群表现出了更多的蝎虫特征。虽然这导致出现了许多畸变现象，但是其强大的毒性似乎让一切都显得值得。 /// As one of the original zerg broods, Leviathan vipers exhibit more defiler tendencies than the rest of the Swarm. While this has caused many abnormalities to surface, its potent toxins appear to be worth it.=16717
Skin/Info/VoidRay,作为圣堂武士与奈拉齐姆科技融合的结晶，虚空辉光舰是极具破坏力的攻击舰船。它的出现证明了两大阵营为一个共同的目标联手协作是完全可行的。 /// The result of combining Templar and Nerazim technology, void rays are devastating assault ships that demonstrate what is possible when the two factions unite for a common cause.=16718
Skin/Info/VoidRayGolden,最新的虚空辉光舰将古代圣堂武士经典的建造改良技术，与奈拉齐姆钟意的暗影色调结合了起来。 /// The latest void rays have combined the classical refinement of ancient Templar construction with the shadowy coloration favored by the Nerazim.=16719
Skin/Info/VoidRayIhanrii,一支陨石舰队突然降临在泰拉多尔九号星上，喷出尖啸的虚空能量光束，将正要击溃新迦南防御力量的塞伯鲁斯异虫打个措手不及。 /// On Tyrador IX, a fleet of stone ships with shrieking void-energy beams appeared and blindsided the Cerberus zerg just as they overran New Canaan's defenses. =16720
Skin/Info/VoidRayPurifier,净化者的虚空辉光舰是工程学上的一个伟大成就，它将三个不同星灵派系的研究成果融合成了同一种造型优美的战舰。 /// The Purifier void ray is a true feat in engineering, combining the research of three different protoss factions in a single elegant vessel.=16721
Skin/Info/VoidRayTaldarim,血水晶是极其不容易收集的。如果塔达林没有足够的血水晶来将虚空辉光舰转变成毁灭者，他们会毫不犹豫地使用该战舰的现有武装。 /// Bloodshard crystals are not easily collected. When the Tal'darim do not have enough of them to convert a void ray into a destroyer, they make use of the ship's existing armaments without hesitation.=16722
Skin/Info/WarpPrism,作为导体连接灵能矩阵的折跃棱镜，既可以充当机动士兵运输船又可以变成应急能量源。尽管它们很脆弱，但是没有它们的星灵舰队是不完整的。 /// By acting as a conduit into the psionic matrix, warp prisms function as both mobile troop transport and emergency power source. Though they are fragile, no protoss fleet is complete without them.=16723
Skin/Info/WarpPrismGolden,古代圣堂武士折跃棱镜具有一种非常特别的水晶晶格，其特殊之处就在于它有时候甚至能反射出其所运载的战士的神经图案。 /// Ancient Templar warp prisms featured a distinctive crystal lattice that would sometimes reflect the neural patterns of the warriors they transport.=16724
Skin/Info/WarpPrismIhanrii,展开的伊罕利折跃棱镜会唤起星灵们对一种花的回忆，这种花曾经长满了他们家乡的山坡，只是那里已经换了一个新的名字——泰拉多尔九号星。 /// Unfurled, the Ihan-rii warp prism evokes a flower that once covered the hillsides of their homeworld, referred to by its current residents as "Tyrador IX."  =16725
Skin/Info/WarpPrismNerazim,达拉姆相位技师有了新突破，现在折跃棱镜可以使用虚空能量了。这些变种被称为相位棱镜，已经在奈拉齐姆指挥官中获得了极高的人气。 /// Daelaam phase-smiths have broken new ground by adapting warp prisms to use Void energy. These variants, known as phase prisms, have already earned great popularity with Nerazim commanders.=16726
Skin/Info/WarpPrismPurifier,如果有必要的话，净化者的折跃棱镜可以将一个智能人格在不同的机体之间进行自动传输，而折跃棱镜可以让这一切发生在战场上的各地。 /// Purifier warp prisms can automatically transfer an AI personality between different shells if needed, and warp prisms enable this to happen anywhere on the battlefield. =16727
Skin/Info/WarpPrismTaldarim,是否给折跃棱镜装备高级武器一直是舰队领主之间争论的焦点。对于其中一部分人而言，能够直接向战场输送部队就已足以。 /// Arming warp prisms with advanced weaponry is a point of contention among the fleet lords. Some prefer to use them to simply deploy their own warriors onto the battlefield.=16728
Skin/Info/WidowMine,最初由维克多·卡琴斯基发明的寡妇雷，现已被优化成极其致命的军事设备。它可以对任何可疑的目标发射防御性飞弹。 /// Initially developed by Victor Kachinsky, the widow mine has been refined into a surprisingly lethal device that can fire defensive missiles against unsuspecting enemies.=16729
Skin/Info/WidowMineCovertOps,饱受走火事故困扰的技术人员决定给寡妇雷增加防护性更好的板甲，以便能防止事故发生，减少意外伤亡。 /// Perplexed by occasional misfires in the past, technicians have added more protective plating to the widow mines to better contain accidents and protect against unintended injuries.=16730
Skin/Info/WidowMineJunker,经过若干轮的超强破坏力实验后，米拉的雇佣兵们重新设计了他们的寡妇雷，以便能装纳额外的武器和炸药。 /// After several rounds of heavily destructive experimentation, Mira's mercs redesigned their widow mines to accommodate additional weaponry and explosives.=16731
Skin/Info/WidowMineSilver,尽管不时就有各种血淋淋的事故成为新闻，但在泰拉多尔九号星的上流社会里，光滑闪亮的寡妇雷仍然被许多人当做宠物。 /// Despite gory accidents that make the news from time to time, sleek and shiny widow mines remain a common pet in the upper-class households of Tyrador IX.=16732
Skin/Info/WidowMineUmojan,一直钟情于机器人技术的尤摩扬工程师们举行了一场特殊比赛，以图造出最完美的寡妇雷机器人。然而令他们震惊的是，最终的优胜者竟然是一位尚未完成学业的女学生。 /// Always fond of robotics, the Umojan engineers held an exclusive competition to craft the perfect widow mine and were thrilled to discover that the winner was still a student finishing her degree.=16733
Skin/Info/Zealot,狂热者在战场上是一群无可匹敌的战士，他们经受数十年的刻苦训练，只为完善自己的各种战斗技巧。其标志性的灵能之刃是用他们自身的灵能能量形成的。 /// Peerless warriors on the battlefield, zealots undergo decades of intense training in order to perfect their combat skills. Their signature psi-blades are formed with their own psionic energy.=16734
Skin/Info/ZealotGolden,许多狂热者很快就跟随了高阶圣堂武士的脚步，开始纪念星灵黄金时代的一切，包括那个时代的艺术与文化成就。然而，这场运动至今尚未获得官方认可。 /// Many zealots were quick to follow the high templar in celebrating the protoss' golden age, along with its artistic and cultural achievements. However, the movement has received no official recognition thus far.=16735
Skin/Info/ZealotIhanrii,伊罕利星灵的狂热者们相信，萨尔那加终有一天会再度归来，给所有英勇的战士赐予永恒的神性。 /// Zealots of the Ihan-rii protoss believe the xel'naga will return one day to bless valiant warriors with eternal godhood.=16736
Skin/Info/ZealotPurifier,虽然警戒者们没有独立的人格，但是它们全都被编程为与其狂热者同胞们一样的高贵战士。 /// Though they do not possess unique personalities, the sentinels are programmed to be noble warriors equal to their zealot brethren.=16737
Skin/Info/ZealotRemastered,为了展现他们的无畏精神， 许多狂热者在全面战争期间不戴头盔就奔赴战场。这种做法自那以后就被禁止了。 /// To demonstrate their fearlessness, many zealots went without head armor during the Great War. This practice has since been discontinued.=16738
Skin/Info/ZealotTaldarim,在塔达林的升格之链中，地位最低的往往是最渴望证明自己的。塔达林的狂热者绝不是一位可以小觑的对手。 /// The lowest ranking links in the Chain of Ascension are also the ones most eager to prove themselves. A zealot of the Tal'darim is a dangerous foe to face.=16739
Skin/Info/ZealotXPR,虽然最高议会不存在了，但是曾为其军事领导人效命的执政官们仍然忠诚于达拉姆。只要星灵存在一日，他们就会义无反顾地战斗到底。 /// Though the Conclave no longer exists, the praetors who served as its military leaders are still loyal to the Daelaam. For as long as the protoss live, they will continue to fight with valor.=16740
Skin/Info/Zergling,跳虫极为凶猛狂暴，尤其是在被更高级的异虫生物指挥，成群结队地发起攻击时是最危险的。 /// Savage and feral, zerglings are most dangerous when attacking in large groups that are controlled by a larger and more advanced strain of zerg.=16741
Skin/Info/ZerglingMecha,尽管外形和动作与真正的跳虫别无二致，但是这些仿生异虫是纯机械复制品，完全依靠电力能源运行，而非吸收敌人的DNA。 /// Though they look and act just like zerglings, the simulants are purely mechanical reproductions that run wholly on electrical power sources, rather than absorbing the DNA of their enemies.=16742
Skin/Info/ZerglingPrimal,一些体型较小的原始跳虫一直以来都被认为和它们在虫群中的同行们别无二致，甚至它们的攻击能力都大同小异。 /// Some of the smaller primal zerglings have been known to resemble their counterparts in the Swarm, even to the point where they possess similar attack capabilities.=16743
Skin/Info/ZerglingRCZ,跳虫的神经系统是如此的高度亢奋，塞伯鲁斯工程师们不得不加装两根新的触角天线才能控制它们正常移动。 /// Zergling nervous systems are so hyperactive that Cerberus engineers had to affix two antennas to control their movement properly.=16744
Skin/Info/ZerglingWebby,跳虫的基因组缺失产生了不可预知的后果。目前在利维坦跳虫身上的生长并不是有意进化，而是它们极度简化的DNA所带来的副作用。 /// The reduction of the zergling genome has had unpredictable results. The growths present on Leviathan zerglings are not intentionally evolved, but a byproduct of their extremely simplified DNA.=16745
Skin/Info/ZerglingXPR,很少有哪种异虫会比跳虫的生命周期更短。出现任何有可能延续生命的变异现象，都是值得观察和分析的。 /// Few zerg have a shorter life expectancy than the zergling. Any mutation that appears to increase that life expectancy is considered worthy of observation and analysis.=16746

UI/HelpGameMechanic_FogOfWar_Description,<ul indent="2" text="▪"><li>战场迷雾让玩家只能看到他拥有的单位和建筑的视野所及之处。</li><li>当玩家失去某块区域的视野时，便不再能看到敌方单位，不过建筑仍将会按照最后所见的状态显示在地图上。</li><li>当玩家遭到来自无视野区域敌人的攻击时，攻击单位将会被显示，但玩家必须拥有视野才能反击。比如说：当一个玩家的单位遭到视野外的攻城坦克轰击时，攻城坦克会在战场迷雾中短暂显示。</li></ul> /// <ul indent="2" text="•"><li>Fog of War limits players' vision to what their units and structures can see.</li><li>When a player loses vision of an area, enemy units can't be seen and structures are shown in the last seen state and location.</li><li>If a player is attacked by an enemy they can't see, they will be shown the attacking unit but can't retaliate until they have vision. Example: If a siege tank is attacking outside of your vision, the siege tank is displayed briefly through the fog of war.</li></ul>=18244

UI/HelpGameMechanic_HighLowGround_Description,<ul indent="2" text="▪"><li>你必须拥有视野才能进攻处于高地上的单位。</li><li>当高地上的单位对你发动攻击时，他们会短暂出现在你的视野中。但你必须拥有完整的视野才能进行反击。</li><li>你可以通过向高地派遣地面部队或使用飞行单位来打开视野。</li></ul></s> /// <ul indent="2" text="•"><li>You must have vision of the high ground in order to attack units on a higher cliff level.</li><li>Units on high ground appear through the fog of war if they attack you, but you can't counterattack unless you have vision of the high ground.</li><li>To gain vision of the high ground, you need a ground unit on the high ground or a flying unit to act as a spotter.</li></ul></s>=18246
